var book = {
	"name": "Joshua",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda la ïap u Moses u shakri U Trai, U Trai u la kren ha u Joshua u khun u Nun, uba u shakri u Moses, U da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “U Moses u shakri jong nga u la ïap; namar kata te, to ïeng, to leit sha shiliang kane ka Jordan, ma me, bad une u paidbah baroh, sha kata ka ri ba nga ai ha ki, ha ki khun Israel keiñ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kat ka jaka baroh ba ka poh'jat jong phi kan ïuh, ïa kata nga la ai ha phi, kumba nga la ong ha u Moses.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naduh ka ri khlaw, bad une u Lebanon, jin haduh ka wah bah, ka wah Ïuphratis keiñ, ka ri ki Hit baroh, haduh ka duriaw bah shaphang sepngi, kan long ka pud jong phi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yn ym don uwei uba lah ban ïeng ha khmat jong me baroh ki sngi ka rta jong me: kumba nga la don ryngkat bad u Moses, kumta ngan don bad me ruh: ngan ym iehnoh ïa me, lymne ngan ym kyntait ïa me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Pynkhlaiñ bad pynshlur bha ïa lade: namar men pynïoh bynta ha une u paidbah ïa kata ka ri ba nga la smai ha ki kpa jong ki ban ai ha ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tang ba men long uba khlaiñ bad uba shlur bha, ba me lah ban sumar ban leh katba kum ïa ka hukum baroh, ba u Moses u shakri jong nga u la hukum ïa me: wat phai noh na ka sha kamon lymne sha kadiang, ba men ïoh man bha kat sha kaba me leit.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wat ai ba kane Ka Kitab Ka Hukum kan jah noh na ka shyntur jong me, hynrei, men ïaipyrkhat ïa ka, synñia sngi, khnang ba men ïoh sumar ban leh katba kum ïa baroh ba la thoh ha ka: naba kumta, men roi ha la ka lynti, bad kumta, men man bha.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hato ngam shym la hukum ïa me? To long uba khlaiñ bad uba shlur bha; wat tieng, lymne wat kyiuh: namar U Trai U Blei jong me u don ryngkat bad me kat sha kaba me leit.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua u la hukum ïa ki rangbah synshar ki paidbah, u da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “To ïaid lyngba ïa ki dara, bad hukum ïa u paidbah, da ong, ‘Pynkhreh ïa ki jingbam; namar ha ki lai sngi phin leit sha shiliang kane ka Jordan, ban leit ïa ka ban ïoh ïa kata ka ri, ïa kaba U Trai U Blei jong phi u ai ha phi ïa ka ban ïoh kynti.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ha ki Reuben, bad ha ki Gad, bad ha ki shiteng jaid Manasseh, u Joshua u la kren, u da ong,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “To kynmaw ïa kata ka ktien ba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum ha phi, u da ong, ‘U Trai U Blei jong phi u ai ha phi ka jingshongthait, bad un ai ha phi ïa kane ka ri.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki tnga jong phi, bad ki khun rit jong phi, bad ki jingri jong phi, kin sah ha kane ka ri ba u Moses u la ai ha phi ha kane ka liang ka Jordan; hynrei, phi baroh ki bashlur, ba la kieng atiar, phin leit sha shiliang ha shuwa ki para jong phi, bad phin ïarap ïa ki;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ha ban da U Trai u la ai ka jingshongthait ha ki para jong phi, kumba ha phi, bad ba ki ruh ki la ïoh ïa kata ka ri kaba U Trai U Blei jong phi u ai ha ki: hadien kata, phin phai sha ka ri ka bynta jong phi, bad phin ïoh ïa ka ruh, ïa kaba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la ai ha phi ha kane ka liang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u Joshua, ki la ong, “Ïa baroh ba me la hukum ïa ngi, ngin leh, bad kat shaba men phah ïa ngi, ngin leit ruh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumba ngi la sngap ïa u Moses ha kiei kiei baroh, kumta, ngin sngap ïa me ruh: tang ba U Trai U Blei jong me un don ryngkat bad me, kumba u la don ryngkat bad u Moses.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Jar uba ïaleh pyrshah ïa ka hukum jong me, bad u ban ym sngap ïa ki ktien jong me ha baroh ba me hukum ïa u, yn pynïap ïa uta: tang ba men long khlaiñ bad shlur bha.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Joshua u khun u Nun u la phah ar ngut ki briew jar jar na Shittim ban syntiat, u da ong, “Khie leit jngoh ïa ka ri, bad ïa ka Jerikho.” Te ki la leit, bad ki la poi ruh ha ka ïing kawei ka nuti kaba kyrteng “ka Rahab,” bad ki la shong basa hangta.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u syiem ka Jerikho, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih, la wan ki briew shane ha kane ka miet na ki khun Israel ban syntiat ïa ka ri.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u syiem ka Jerikho u la phah ha ka Rahab, u da ong, “To wallam noh ïa kita ki briew ba la wan ha pha, kiba la rung ha ïing jong pha: namar ki la wan ban syntiat ïa ka ri baroh.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, kata ka kynthei ka la shim ïa kita ki ar ngut ki briew bad ka la buhrieh ïa ki; ka la ong ruh, “La wan kita ki briew ha nga shisha, hynrei, ngam shym tip kiba na-ei:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ka la jia ruh hamar ka por ban khang ïa ka khyrdop, haba ka la dum, ba kita ki briew ki la leit noh: shano kita ki briew ki la leit, ngam tip shuh: beh kloi nadien jong ki; namar phin lap ïa ki.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei ka, ka la lah lam ïa ki, shalor ïing, bad ka la buhrieh ïa ki da ki dieng 'saihon, ïa kiba ka la lah thad ter ter halor ïing.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la beh nadien jong ki ha lynti ka Jordan haduh ka jaka khriang: te ki tang shu lah mih kita kiba la beh nadien jong ki, la khang ïa ka khyrdop.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad haba kim pat thiah, ka la wan kiew sha ki, shalor ïing;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ka la ong ruh ha kita ki briew, “Nga tip ba U Trai u la ai ha phi ïa kane ka ri, bad ba ka jingsheptieng ïa phi ka la hap halor jong ngi, bad baroh ki trai-shnong kane ka ri kim don mynsiem shuh ïa phi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar ngi la ïohsngew kumno U Trai u la pynrngad ïa ka um ka Duriaw Basaw ha shuwa jong phi, mynba phi la mih noh na Ijipt; bad kumno phi la leh ïa ar ngut ki syiem ki Amor, kiba ha shiliang ka Jordan, u Sihon bad u Og keiñ, ïa kiba phi la pynjot thiaw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te katba ngi la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki dohnud jong ngi ki la um, lymne ha uno uno ruh ym sah mynsiem shuh ïa phi: naba U Trai U Blei jong phi u long U Blei ha bneng sha jrong, bad ha ka khyndew shapoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te namar kata, nga duwai ha phi, to smai ha nga da U Trai, namar ba nga la leh isynei ïa phi, ba phi ruh phin leh isynei ïa ka ïing u kpa jong nga, bad ba phin ai ka dak kaba shisha ha nga:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ba phin pynim ïa u kpa jong nga bad ïa ka kmie jong nga, bad ïa ki para jong nga kynthei bad shynrang, bad ïa baroh ba ki don, bad ba phin pyllait ïa ki mynsiem jong ngi na ka jingïap.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la ïathuh ha ka, “Ka jingim jong ngi namar ka jong phi, lada phin ym pynpaw ïa kane ka kam jong ngi; kan long ruh, haba U Trai un ai ïa kane ka ri ha ngi, ba ngin leh isynei bad kaba shisha ïa phi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la pynhiar ïa ki da u tyllai na ka jingkhang ïit: namar ka ïing jong ka, ka la don ha ka kynroh shnong, bad ka la shong ïing halor kata ka kynroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka la ong ruh ha ki, “Khie leit sha u lum, ïoh ba ki nongbeh kin ïashem ïa phi; buhrieh ïa lade ruh hangta lai sngi, ha ban da wan noh kita ki nongbeh; te hadien kata, phin leit ha la ka lynti.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la ong ha ka, “Ngin long kiba lait na kane ka jingsmai jong pha ïa kaba pha la pynsmai ïa ngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha khmih, ynda ngin wan sha kane ka ri, phan teh ïa une u 'sai saw na kata ka jingkhang ïit na kaba pha la pynhiar ïa ngi: ïalum ruh ïa la u kpa bad ïa la ka kmie, bad ïa la ki para, bad ïa baroh ba dei ïa u kpa jong pha, ha pha ha kane ka ïing.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kan long ruh, ba jar uba mih na ki jingkhang ka ïing jong pha sha lynti shnong, ka snam jong u kan long halor ka khlieh jong u hi, bad ngi ngin long khlem jingrem: bad jar ba don lem bad pha ha ïing, ka snam jong u kan long halor ka khlieh jong ngi, lada yn buh ka kti ha u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te lada phan pynpaw ïa kane ka kam jong ngi, ynda kumta, ngi la lait na ka jingsmai jong pha ïa kaba pha la pynsmai ïa ngi.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “To kan long kumta katba kum ka ktien jong phi.” Ka la phah noh ïa ki, bad ki la leit noh. Bad ka la teh ïa uta u 'sai saw ha kata ka jingkhang ïit.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la leit, bad ki la ïapoi ha uta u lum, ki la sah ruh hangta lai sngi, ha ban da kita ki nongbeh ki la wan noh: bad kita ki nongbeh ki la wad ïa ki baroh shilynter ka lynti, hynrei, kim shym shem.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, kita ar ngut ki briew ki la leit wan noh, bad ki la hiar na uta u lum, bad ki la leit sha shiliang ruh, bad ki la wan ha u Joshua u khun u Nun; bad ki la ïathuh ruh ha u ïa kiei kiei baroh ba la jia ha ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki la ong ha u Joshua, “Da shisha U Trai u la ai ha ki kti jong ngi ïa kata ka ri baroh; namar ki trai-shnong baroh ruh ha kata ka ri kim don mynsiem shuh ïa ngi.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Joshua u la khie dang step, bad ki la ïamih na Shittim, bad ki la ïapoi sha Jordan, ma u bad ki khun Israel baroh; bad ki la shong shuwa hangta, ki sa ryngkang sha shiliang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka la jia ruh ynda la lai sngi, ba ki rangbah ki la ïaid lyngba ïa ki dara;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ki la hukum ïa u paidbah, ki da ong, “Haba phi ïohi ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai U Blei jong phi, bad ba ki lyngdoh ki Lebi ki da bah ïa ka, ynda kumta, phin ïeng na ka jaka jong phi, bad phin leit hadien jong ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, phin kham pajih hapdeng jong phi bad ka, kumba ar hajar pruh da ka jingthew: wat wan hajan jong ka, ba phin tip ïa ka lynti da kaba phin ïaid; naba phim ju ïaid na kane ka lynti mynno mynno ruh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha u paidbah, “To pynkyntang ïa lade; namar lashai U Trai un leh ïa ki jingphylla hapdeng jong phi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Joshua u la kren ruh ha ki lyngdoh, u da ong, “To ïarah ïa ka synduk ka jutang, bad leit sha shiliang ha shuwa u paidbah.” Te ki la ïarah ïa ka synduk ka jutang, bad ki la leit ha shuwa u paidbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Ha kane ka sngi, ngan sdang ban pynkhraw ïa me ha khmat ki Israel baroh, ba kin ïoh tip ba, kumba nga la don ryngkat bad u Moses, kumta, ngan don ryngkat bad me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad men hukum ïa ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa ka synduk ka jutang, da ong, ‘Haba phi la poi harud ka um ka Jordan, phin sangeh ha ka Jordan.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha ki khun Israel, “Ale shane, bad to sngap ïa ki ktien U Trai U Blei jong phi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong ruh, “Da kane phin tip ba U Blei u ba-im u don hapdeng jong phi, bad ba da shisha un beh ha shuwa jong phi ïa ki Kanaan, bad ïa ki Hit, bad ïa ki Hib, bad ïa ki Peris, bad ïa ki Girgash, bad ïa ki Amor, bad ïa ki Jebus.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha khmih, ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ka pyrthei baroh ka leit ha shuwa jong phi sha Jordan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mynta te, to shim khat-ar ngut ki rangbah na ki jaid Israel, uwei uwei u rangbah na kawei ka jaid.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kan jia ruh ba, katba ki poh'jat ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa ka synduk U Trai, U Trai ka pyrthei baroh keiñ, kin ïeng ha ki um ka Jordan, ba ïa ki um ka Jordan yn pynkhlad noh, kata, ïa ki um kiba hiar na neng; bad kin ïeng kum ka kynton.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ki paidbah ki la ïamih na la ki ïingjaiñ, ban leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa ka synduk ka jutang ki ha shuwa u paidbah;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad haba kita kiba bah ïa ka synduk ki la poi ha Jordan, bad ba ki poh'jat kita ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa ka synduk ki la dei ha ka rmiang ka um, (namar ka Jordan ka ju shlei miar baroh ka aïom ot,)",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> te kita ki um kiba hiar na neng ki la ïeng, bad ki la ïeng kum ka kynton, kham sha jngai eh, hajan ka shnong Adam, kaba ha syndah ka Sarethan: bad kita kiba hiar sha ka duriaw ka madan, ka Duriaw Mluh keiñ, ki la duh khoit: kumta, u paidbah u la leit sha shiliang marpyrshah ka Jerikho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ki la ïeng skhem ha ryngkew hapdeng ka Jordan, bad ki Israel baroh ki la leit sha shiliang na ryngkew, ha ban da u paidbah baroh u la leit phar sha shiliang ka Jordan."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda u paidbah baroh phar u la ryngkang sha shiliang ka Jordan, U Trai u la kren ha u Joshua, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Shim phi khat-ar ngut ki briew na u paidbah, uwei uwei u briew na kawei ka jaid keiñ,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad to hukum ïa ki, da ong, ‘To shim phi nangne napdeng ka Jordan, na kata ka jaka ha kaba ki sla'jat ki lyngdoh ki la ïeng skhem, khat-ar tylli ki maw, phin rah ïa ki ruh sha shiliang ryngkat bad phi, to buh ruh ïa ki ha kata ka jaka sah miet, ha kaba phin sah ha kane ka miet keiñ.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua u la khot ïa kita ki khat-ar ngut, kiba u la khreh lypa na ki khun Israel, uwei uwei u briew na kawei ka jaid:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Joshua u la ong ruh ha ki, “To leit sha shiliang ha shuwa ka synduk U Trai U Blei jong phi shapdeng ka Jordan, to rah ruh uwei uwei baroh na phi ïa la u maw halor la ka tyrpeng, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki jaid ki khun Israel:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ba kane kan ïoh long ka dak hapdeng jong phi, ba haba ki khun jong phi kin kylli lashai lashisngi, da kaba ong, ‘Da kine ki maw phi mut aïu?’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, phin ïathuh ha ki, ‘La pyndkut noh ïa ki um ka Jordan ha shuwa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai; mynba ka la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, ïa ki um ka Jordan la pyndkut noh: bad kine ki maw kin long ka jingkynmaw ïa ki khun Israel junom.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la leh kumta kumba u Joshua u la hukum, ki la shim ruh ïa ki khat-ar tylli ki maw napdeng ka Jordan, kumba U Trai u la kren ha u Joshua, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki jaid ki khun Israel; ki la rah ruh ïa ki sha shiliang ryngkat bad ki sha kata ka jaka ha kaba ki la sah miet, bad ki la buh ïa ki hangta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joshua u la pynïeng khat-ar tylli ki maw hapdeng ka Jordan, ha kata ka jaka ha kaba ki sla'jat kita ki lyngdoh kiba la bah ïa kata ka synduk ka jutang ki la ïeng: ki don hangta ruh, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa kata ka synduk ki la ïeng hapdeng ka Jordan, ha ban da la pyndep ïa baroh ba la hukum U Trai ha u Joshua ban kren ha u paidbah, katba kum ïa baroh ba la hukum u Moses ha u Joshua: te uta u paidbah u la kyrkieh bad u la leit sha shiliang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda uta u paidbah baroh phar u la leit sha shiliang, kata ka synduk U Trai ruh ka la leit sha shiliang, bad kita ki lyngdoh, ha khmat uta u paidbah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki khun u Reuben, bad ki khun u Gad, bad ka shiteng ka jaid Manasseh ruh, ki la leit sha shiliang kiba la kieng atiar, ha khmat ki khun Israel, kumba u Moses u la kren ha ki:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kumba sawphew hajar ba la kieng atiar ban hiar thma ki la leit ha khmat U Trai sha ka thma, sha ki madan Jerikho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha kata ka sngi, U Trai u la pyndonburom ïa u Joshua ha khmat ki Israel baroh; te ki la sheptieng ïa u, kumba ki la ju sheptieng ïa u Moses, baroh ki sngi ka rta jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Joshua, u da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “To hukum ïa kita ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa kata ka synduk ka jingphla, ba kin ïawan kiew na Jordan.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kata, u Joshua u la hukum ïa kita ki lyngdoh, u da ong, “To wan kiew noh na Jordan.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba kita ki lyngdoh kiba bah ïa kata ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ki la kiew noh napdeng ka Jordan, bad ba ki sla'jat kita ki lyngdoh ki la kiew sha ryngkew, ki um ka Jordan ki la phai pat sha la ka jaka, bad ki la shlei ïa la ki rud baroh, kumba mynshuwa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad uta u paidbah u la kiew na Jordan ha ka bashiphew sngi jong u bnai u banyngkong, bad ki la shong dara ha Gilgal, ha ka pud kaba shaphang mihngi jong ka Jerikho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ïa kita ki khat-ar tylli ki maw, ïa kiba ki la rah na Jordan, u Joshua u la thung ha Gilgal.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la kren ruh ha ki khun Israel, u da ong, “Haba ki khun jong phi kin sa kylli lashai lashisngi; da kaba ong, ‘Kine ki maw ki mut aïu?’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, phin pyntip ha la ki khun, da kaba ong, ‘Ki Israel ki la ryngkang ïa kane ka Jordan na ryngkew.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Naba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la pynrngad ïa ki um ka Jordan ha shuwa jong phi, ha ban da phi la leit sha shiliang, kumba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la leh ïa ka Duriaw Basaw, ïa kaba u la pynrngad na shuwa jong ngi, ha ban da ngi la leit sha shiliang:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ba ki bynriew baroh ha ka pyrthei kin dup ithuh ïa ka kti U Trai, ba ka long kaba don bor; ba kin dup sheptieng ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi junom.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba baroh ki syiem ki Amor, kiba sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang sepngi, bad baroh ki syiem ki Kanaan, kiba hajan ka duriaw, ki la ïohsngew ba U Trai u la pynrngad ïa ki um ka Jordan ha shuwa ki khun Israel, ha ban da ki la ïaleit sha shiliang, kumta ki dohnud jong ki, ki la um noh, ba ym don mynsiem shuh ha ki, namar ki khun Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ha kata ka por, U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “To thaw ïa me ki tari maw, bad otsher pat ïa ki khun Israel ha ka ba-ar sien.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Joshua u la thaw ha u ki tari maw, bad u la otsher ïa ki khun Israel ha u lum Haaralot.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kane ka daw balei ba u Joshua u la otsher: ki briew baroh, ki shynrang, ki nongïapom baroh keiñ, kiba la wan mih noh na ri Ijipt, ki la lah ïap ha ri khlaw ha lynti, ynda ki la mih noh na Ijipt.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar ïa ki briew baroh ba la mih noh la otsher: hynrei, ïa ki briew baroh ba la kha ha ka ri khlaw ha lynti ynda ki la mih na Ijipt, ïa kita ym pat shym la otsher.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar ki khun Israel ki la ïaid ha ri khlaw sawphew snem, ha ban da u paidbah baroh, kiba long ki nongïapom kiba la mih na Ijipt, ki la duh noh khoit, namar ba kim shym la kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai: ha kiba u la smai ba un ym shah ba kin ïohi ïa kata ka ri kaba U Trai u la smai ha ki kpa jong ki ba un ai ha ngi, ka ri kaba tuid da ka dud bad ka ngap keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kita ki khun jong ki, kiba u la pynmih ha ka jaka jong ki, ïa kita, u Joshua u la otsher: naba ki long ki bym shym la otsher namar ba ym shym la otsher ïa ki ha lynti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ynda la lah otsher ïa ki briew baroh, ki la sah ha la ki jaka ha ka dara, ha ban da ki la koit.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Ha kane ka sngi nga la pyntyllun noh na phi ïa ka rain ka Ijipt.” Namar kata, u la kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “ka Gilgal,” haduh mynta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la shong dara ha Gilgal; bad ki la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Ka Jinglait ha ka bakhatsaw sngi jong uta u bnai mynmiet ha ki madan Jerikho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki la bam ruh da u Kew rim kata ka ri kum lashai hadien Ka Niam Ka Jinglait, ki kpu bakhlem thiat bad u shira, ha kajuh ka sngi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te kata ka manna ka la wai noh kum lashai, ynda ki la bam da uta u Kew rim kata ka ri; bad ki khun Israel kim shym ïoh manna shuh; hynrei, ki la bam da u soh ka ri Kanaan ha kata ka snem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u Joshua u la hajan ka Jerikho, u la khmied ïa la ki khmat bad u la khmih, te, ha khmih, la ïeng u briew ha marpyrshah jong u la ka talwar ba la sei ha ka kti: te u Joshua u la leit sha u, bad u la ong ha u, “Me ha ka liang jong ngi, ne ha ka liang ki nongïaleh ïa ngi?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u la ong, “Em; hynrei kum u kaptan jong u paidïapom jong U Trai nga la wan mynta.” Bad u Joshua u la dem ngon la ka khmat ha khyndew, bad u la mane, bad u la ong ha u, “U Kynrad jong nga u ong aïu ha la u shakri?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta u kaptan jong u paidïapom jong U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “To loit noh la ki juti na la ki sla'jat; namar kata ka jaka ha kaba me ïeng ka bakhuid.” Te u Joshua u la leh kumta."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> (Te ïa ka Jerikho la khang khop namar ki khun Israel: ym don ba mih shabar, lane ba rung shapoh.)",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Ha khmih, nga la ai ha ka kti jong me ïa ka Jerikho, bad ïa u syiem jong ka, bad ki rangbah bakhrawbor.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki paidïapom baroh phin tawiar ïa ka shnong, da kaba ïaid sawdong ïa ka shnong shi sien. Kumta men leh hynriew sngi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad hynñiew ngut ki lyngdoh kin rah ha shuwa ka synduk, hynñiew tylli ki turoi jubili: bad ha ka bahynñiew ka sngi phin ïaid sawdong ïa ka shnong, hynñiew sien, bad kita ki lyngdoh kin put da kita ki turoi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba yn put kynsan da kita ki turoi jubili, bad haba phin ïohsngew ka jingsawa kata ka turoi, u paidbah baroh un risa da ka jingrisa bajam; te ka kynroh ka shnong kan kyllon kram, bad uta u paidbah un kiew uwei uwei baroh pyrshah beit ïa u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Joshua u khun u Nun u la khot ïa kita ki lyngdoh, bad u la ong ha ki, “To rah ïa ka synduk ka jutang, to ai ruh ba hynñiew ngut ki lyngdoh kin rah ïa ki hynñiew tylli ki turoi jubili ha shuwa ka synduk U Trai.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “To khie leit, to ïaid sawdong ruh ïa ka shnong, bad kita kiba kieng atiar kin nang ïaid sha shuwa ka synduk U Trai.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te haba u Joshua u la kren ha uta u paidbah kumta, kita ki hynñiew ngut ki lyngdoh kiba rah ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki turoi jubili ha khmat U Trai ki la nang ïaid, bad ki la put da kita ki turoi: bad kata ka synduk ka jutang U Trai ka la bud ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kita kiba kieng atiar ki la nang ïaid sha shuwa kita ki lyngdoh kiba put ïa kita ki turoi, bad uta u paidbah bakhatduh u la ïaid hadien kata ka synduk, kita ki lyngdoh ki da ïaid ïa-put artad ïa kita ki turoi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Joshua u la hukum ïa uta u paidbah, u da ong, “Phin ym risa, lymne wat ai ba yn ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong phi, lymne kan ym mih shikyntien na ka shyntur jong phi, haduh kata ka sngi ba ngan hukum ïa phi ban risa; hangta phin sa risa.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, ïa kata ka synduk U Trai u la pynïaid tawiar ïa ka shnong, da kaba ïaid sawdong ïa ka shi sien; bad ki la wan sha ka dara, ki la shong ruh ha ka dara.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Joshua u la khie dang step, bad kita ki lyngdoh ki la bah ïa ka synduk U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad kita ki hynñiew ngut ki lyngdoh kiba rah ïa kita ki hynñiew tylli ki turoi jubili ha shuwa ka synduk U Trai ki la ïai-ïaid, bad ki la put da kita ki turoi: bad kita kiba kieng atiar ki la nang ïaid sha shuwa jong ki; hynrei, uta u paidbah bakhatduh u la bud nadien kata ka synduk U Trai, bad kita ki lyngdoh ki la nang ïaid ïa-put artad da kita ki turoi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ha ka sngi ka ba-ar ruh ki la tawiar ïa ka shnong shi sien, bad ki la leit phai sha ka dara: kumta, ki la leh hynriew sngi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ha ka bahynñiew ka sngi, ki la khie dang step haba dang shai byrngut, bad ki la tawiar ïa kata ka shnong kumjuh hynñiew sien: tang ha kata ka sngi ki la tawiar ïa ka shnong, hynñiew sien.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ha ka bahynñiew sien, haba kita ki lyngdoh ki la put da kita ki turoi, u Joshua u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “To ïarisa; namar U Trai u la ai ïa kata ka shnong ha phi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kata ka shnong kan long kaba la tim ha U Trai, ma ka bad baroh katba don ha ka: tang ka Rahab ka nuti kan im, ma ka bad baroh kiba bad ka ha ïing, namar ka la buhrieh ïa kita ki nonglam-ktien kiba ngi la phah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Phi te, la kumno kumno phin kyndiah noh ïa lade na kata kaba la tim, ba ïoh phi hi phin long kiba la tim haba phi shim na kata kaba la tim; kumta phin pynlong ka jingtim ïa ka dara ki Israel, bad phin pynjynjar ïa ka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ka rupa bad ka ksiar, bad ki khiew ki pliang rnong bad nar baroh, ki long ba la kyntang ha U Trai: kita kin leit sha ka jingkynshew U Trai.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, uta u paidbah u la risa, bad kita ki lyngdoh ki la put da kita ki turoi: te haba uta u paidbah u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa kata ka turoi, kumta, uta u paidbah u la risa da ka jingrisa bajam, te kata ka kynroh ka la kyllon kram, ba kumta uta u paidbah u la kiew sha shnong, uwei uwei baroh keiñ marpyrshah beit ïa u, bad ki la jop ïa kata ka shnong.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la pynjot thiaw ïa baroh ba la don ha kata ka shnong, shynrang bad kynthei, khynnah bad tymmen, bad masi dab, bad langbrot, bad kadda, da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u Joshua u la ong ha kita ki ar ngut ki briew kiba la leit ban syntiat ïa kata ka ri, “Khie leit ha ka ïing kata ka nuti, bad wallam noh nangta ïa kata ka briew, bad ïa baroh ba ka don, kumba phi la smai ha ka.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, kita ki samla kiba la long nongsyntiat ki la rung, bad ki la wallam ruh ïa ka Rahab, bad ïa u kpa jong ka bad ïa ka kmie jong ka, bad ïa ki para jong ka, bad ïa baroh ba ka don, bad ki la wallam ïa ki kur jong ka baroh; bad ki la iehnoh ïa ki habar ka dara ki Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki la thang ïa kata ka shnong da ka ding, bad ïa baroh ba la don ha ka: tang ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang rnong bad nar, ki la buh ha ka jingkynshew ka ïing U Trai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ri pynim ïa ka Rahab ka nuti, bad ïa ka ïing u kpa jong ka, bad ïa baroh ba ka la don; bad ka la shong ha Israel haduh kane ka sngi; namar ba ka la buhrieh ïa kita ki nonglam-ktien, ïa kiba u Joshua u la phah ban syntiat ïa ka Jerikho.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Joshua u la pynsmai ïa ki ha kata ka por, u da ong, “Long ba la tim ha khmat U Trai ïa uta u briew uba ïeng bad uba tei ïa kane ka shnong Jerikho: “Da kaba un duh ïa la u khun nyngkong un seng ïa ka nongrim jong ka, bad da kaba un duh ïa la u khun khatduh un pynïeng ïa ki khyrdop jong ka.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumta U Trai u la don lem bad u Joshua; bad ka nam jong u, ka la phriang ïa ka ri baroh."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hynrei, ki khun Israel ki la leh palat ha kata ka basang: namar u Akhan, u khun u Karmi, u khun u Sabdi, u khun u Serah, na ka jaid Judah, u la shim na kata ka basang: bad ka jingbitar U Trai ïa ki khun Israel ka la meh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Joshua u la phah briew na Jerikho sha Ai, kaba hajan Beth-aben, shaphang mihngi na Bethel, bad u la kren ha ki, u da ong, “To leit kiew bad jngoh ïa ka ri.” Te kita ki briew ki la leit kiew bad ki la jngoh ïa ka Ai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la wan phai sha u Joshua, ki la ong ruh ha u, “Wat ai ba ki briew baroh kin leit kiew; tang kumba ar hajar ne lai hajar briew kin leit kiew bad kin jop ïa ka Ai; wat pynshitom ïa ki briew baroh shata, naba ki long khyndiat.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, ki la leit kiew shata na u paidbah kumba lai hajar briew: bad ki la phet ïap na khmat ki briew jong ka Ai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kita ki briew jong ka Ai ki la pynïap na ki kumba laiphew hynriew ngut ki briew; bad ki la beh ïa ki na khmat ka khyrdop haduh Shebarim, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki ha ka riat: te ki dohnud uta u paidbah ki la um, bad ki la long kum ka um.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Joshua u la kad ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la hap dem la ka khmat ha ka khyndew ha khmat ka synduk U Trai haduh janmiet, ma u bad ki tymmen basan ki Israel; bad ki la tep khyndew halor la ki khlieh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong, “Waw! A Trai U Blei, balei ba me la shu wallam ïa une u paidbah sha shiliang Jordan, ban ai noh ïa ngi ha ka kti ki Amor, ban pynjot ïa ngi? A ban da ngi la shu hun, ba ngin da shong ruh sha shiliang ka Jordan!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A Trai, ngan ong aïu, haba ki Israel ki phai dien na khmat ki nongshun!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar ki Kanaan bad ki trai-shnong kiba ha ka ri kin ïohsngew ïa kane, bad kin ker sawdong ïa ngi, kin ot noh ruh ïa ka kyrteng jong ngi na ka khyndew: te men leh kumno ïa la ka kyrteng bakhraw?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “To ïeng joit; balei me hap dem la ka khmat kumne?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> U Israel u la leh pop; bad ki la ryngkang ruh ïa ka jutang jong nga ïa kaba nga la hukum ïa ki: namar ki la shim ïa kata ka basang; bad ki la tuh ruh, bad ki la shukor ruh de, ki la buh ïa ka ruh hapdeng ki jingbuh jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata, ki khun Israel kim lah ïeng ha khmat ki nongshun jong ki, ki phai la ka lyngthohdoh na khmat kita ki nongshun jong ki, naba, ki long kiba la tim: nga ruh ngan ym don ryngkat bad phi shuh, lymda phin pynduh ïa kata ka basang napdeng jong phi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To ïeng noh, pynkhuid ïa u paidbah, to ong ruh, ‘To pynkhuid ïa lade hamar kaba lashai: naba kumne ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, “Don kata ka basang hapdeng jong me, ko Israel: mem lah ban ïeng ha khmat ki nongshun jong me, ha ban da phin pynmih noh ïa kata ka basang napdeng jong phi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, mynstep phin wan hajan katba kum ki jaid jong phi: kan sa long ruh, ba ïa kata ka jaid ïa kaba U Trai un kem, kan wan hajan katba kum ki kur; bad ïa kata ka kur ïa kaba U Trai un kem, kan wan hajan katba kum ki ïing: bad ïa kata ka ïing kaba U Trai un kem, kan wan hajan ha la u briew u briew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kan sa long ruh, ba uta ïa uba yn kem ba don kata ka basang bad u, yn thang ïa u da ka ding, ïa u bad baroh katba u don: namar u la ryngkang ïa ka jutang U Trai, bad namar u la leh ïa ka jingbieit ha Israel.’ ”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la khie dang step, bad u la wallam ïa ki Israel katba kum ki jaid jong ki; te la kem ïa ka jaid Judah:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad u la wallam ïa ki kur u Judah; te u la kem ïa ka kur ki Serah: bad u la wallam ïa ka kur ki Serah ha la u briew u briew; bad la kem ïa u Sabdi:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u la wallam ïa ka ïing jong u ha la u briew u briew; te la kem ïa u Akhan, u khun u Karmi, u khun u Sabdi, u khun u Serah, na ka jaid Judah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha u Akhan, “Ko khun, to ai burom, nga kyrpad ïa me, ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, bad to phla ha u; bad ïathuh ha nga mynta ïa kaei me la leh; wat buhrieh na nga.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Akhan u la ïathuh ha u Joshua, bad u la ong, “Shisha nga la leh pop ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, bad kumne bad kumtai nga la leh:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> haba nga la ïohi hapdeng ki jinglute, ka barandi Babilon ba-itynnad, bad arspah shekel ka rupa, bad shi lyngkhot ka ksiar kaba sanphew shekel da ka jingthew, ynda kumta, nga la ikwah ïa ki, bad nga la shim ïa ki; ha khmih ruh, la buhrieh ïa ki hapoh khyndew hapdeng ka ïingjaiñ jong nga, bad ka rupa hapoh jong ka.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la phah ki briew, bad ki la ïaphet sha kata ka ïingjaiñ; ha khmih ruh, la buhrieh ïa ka ha kata ka ïingjaiñ jong u, bad kata ka rupa hapoh jong ka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la shim ïa kita napdeng kata ka ïingjaiñ, bad ki la wallam ïa ki ha u Joshua, bad ha ki khun Israel baroh; ki la buh ïa ki ruh ha khmat U Trai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Joshua, bad ki Israel baroh lem bad u, ki la shim ïa u Akhan u khun u Serah, bad kata ka rupa, bad kata ka barandi, bad kata ka shi lyngkhot ka ksiar, ïa ki khun shynrang jong u ruh, bad ki khun kynthei, ïa ki masi dab jong u ruh, bad ki kadda jong u, bad ki langbrot jong u, bad ka ïingjaiñ jong u ruh de, bad ïa baroh katba u don: bad ki la wallam ïa ki sha ka them Akhor.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong, “Balei me la pynjynjar ïa ngi? U Trai un pynjynjar ïa me ha kane ka sngi.” Te ki Israel baroh ki la lynthem ïa u da ki maw; bad ki la thang ïa ki da ka ding, ynda ki la lynthem ïa ki da ki maw.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki la kynton ruh halor jong u ka kynton maw ka bakhraw, haduh kane ka sngi; kumta U Trai u la phai noh na kaba shit lep ka jingbitar jong u. Namar kata, la kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka, “ka Them Akhor,” haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Wat sheptieng, lymne wat kyiuh: to shim ïa ki paidïapom baroh bad me, to ïeng ruh, khie leit kiew sha Ai: ha khmih, nga la ai ïa u syiem Ai ha ka kti jong me, bad u paid jong u, ka shnong jong u ruh, bad ka ri jong u ruh de:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> men leh ruh ïa ka Ai bad ïa u syiem jong ka kumba me la leh ïa ka Jerikho bad u syiem jong ka: tang ïa ka jinglute jong ka, bad ki jingri jong ka ruh, phin shim ban long ka jinglute ha lade: buh ka jingap thap ïa ka shnong na shadien jong ka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la ïeng, bad ki paidïapom baroh, ban leit kiew sha Ai: bad u Joshua u la jied laiphew hajar ngut, ki rangbah bashait bad bashlur, bad u la phah noh ïa ki mynmiet.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u la hukum ïa ki, u da ong, “Ha khmih phin thap ïa ka shnong, na shadien ka shnong keiñ: wat leit jngai eh na ka shnong, hynrei, phin long baroh kiba la khreh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ma nga ruh, bad u paidbah baroh uba bad nga, ngin wan hajan ka shnong: te haba kin mih noh ïaleh ïa ngi, kumba mynnyngkong, ngin phet na khmat jong ki;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ki ruh kin wan beh ïa ngi, ha ban da ngi la ring ïa ki na ka shnong; namar kin ong, ‘Ki phet na khmat jong ngi, kumba mynnyngkong;’ kumta ngin phet na khmat jong ki:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ynda kumta, phin mih na kaba thap, bad phin jop ïa ka shnong; naba U Trai U Blei jong phi un aiti ïa ka ha ka kti jong phi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kan sa long ruh, ynda phi la jop ïa ka shnong, ba phin thang ïa ka shnong da ka ding; katba kum ka hukum U Trai phin leh: to khmih, nga la hukum ïa phi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la phah noh ïa ki; ki ruh ki la leit ap thap, bad ki la shong hapdeng ka Bethel bad ka Ai, shaphang sepngi na Ai: hynrei, u Joshua u la sah ha kata ka miet hapdeng u paidbah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Joshua u la khie dang step, bad u la ñiew ïa ki briew, bad u la leit kiew ruh, ma u, bad ki tymmen basan ki Israel, ha shuwa u paidbah sha Ai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kita ki paidïapom baroh kiba bad u, ki la leit kiew, bad ki la leit hajan, bad ki la wan ruh ha khmat ka shnong bad ki la shong dara shaphang shatei jong ka Ai: bad la don ka them hapdeng jong ki bad ka Ai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u la shim kumba san hajar ngut ki briew, bad u la buh ïa ki ban ap thap hapdeng ka Bethel bad ka Ai, shaphang sepngi jong ka shnong.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta, ki la buh ïa kita ki paid, u paid baroh keiñ uba shaphang shatei jong ka shnong, bad ki nongsyntiat jong ki shaphang sepngi jong ka shnong; bad u Joshua u la leit ha kata ka miet shapdeng kata ka them.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u syiem ka Ai u la ïohi ïa kata, ki la kyrkieh bad ki la khie dang step, bad ki briew kata ka shnong ki la mih pyrshah ïa ki Israel, ban ïapom, ma u bad ki briew jong u baroh, ha ka por ba la buh, ha shuwa ka madan; hynrei, um tip ba don kiba ap thap ïa u nadien ka shnong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Joshua bad ki Israel baroh ki la leh kumba ki la shah jop ha khmat jong ki, bad ki la phet na ka lynti ka ri khlaw.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te la ïalum lang ïa ki briew baroh kiba la don ha shnong ban beh nadien jong ki: te ki la beh ïa u Joshua, bad la ring ïa ki na ka shnong.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ym shym la sah shuh uwei u briew ha Ai lane ha Bethel, u bym shym la mih noh ban beh ïa ki Israel: ki la iehnoh rynghang ïa ka shnong, bad ki la beh ïa ki Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Rah ïa uta u sum uba ha ka kti jong me shaphang Ai; namar ngan ai ïa ka ha ka kti jong me.” Te u Joshua u la rah joit ïa uta u sum ba u la don ha la ka kti shaphang kata ka shnong.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te kita ki nongap thap ki la khie buk na la ka jaka, bad u tang shu rah ïa la ka kti ki la mareh shisyndon, ki la rung ruh ha kata ka shnong, bad ki la jop ïa ka; ki la pynkloi ruh, bad ki la thang ïa kata ka shnong da ka ding.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba kita ki nong Ai ki la kyrtiang, ki la ïohi, te ha khmih, ka tdem kata ka shnong ka la kiew sha bneng, te kim don bor shuh ban phet shane ne shawei: bad kita kiba la phet sha ri khlaw ki la phai kylla ïaleh ïa kita ki nongbeh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba u Joshua bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïohi ba kita kiba ap thap ki la jop ïa kata ka shnong, bad ba ka tdem kata ka shnong ka la kiew, ynda kumta, ki la phai pat, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki nong Ai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te kita kiwei ruh ki la mih noh na shnong pyrshah ïa ki, kumta, ki la don hapdeng ki Israel, kiwei ha kane ka liang, bad kiwei pat ha kata kawei ka liang: bad ki la jop ïa ki, ha ban da ym shym la iehnoh ïa uwei na ki ban sah ne ban lait.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa u syiem ka Ai ruh la kem im, bad ki la wallam ïa u ha u Joshua.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ynda ki Israel ki la wai ban pynïap ïa ki nong Ai baroh ha madan, ha ka ri khlaw sha kaba ki la beh ïa ki, bad haba ki la kyllon baroh da ka syrti waitlam, ha ban da ki la duh noh khoit, ki Israel baroh ki la leit phai sha Ai, bad ki la pynduh ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te baroh kiba la kyllon ha kata ka sngi, shynrang bad kynthei, ki la long khat-ar hajar, ki nong Ai baroh keiñ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba u Joshua um shym kynran noh ïa la ka kti, da kaba u la rah ïa uta u sum, ha ban da u la pynduh noh khoit ïa ki nong Ai baroh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tang ki jingri bad ki jinglute jong kata ka shnong ki Israel ki la shim ban long ka jinglute ïa lade, katba kum ka ktien U Trai kaba u la hukum ïa u Joshua.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la thang ïa ka Ai, bad u la pynlong lymbher taid ïa ka junom, ka jaka kynjah keiñ, haduh mynta.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad ïa u syiem ka Ai u la phasi halor u dieng haduh ban da la janmiet: te ynda la sep ka sngi, u Joshua u la hukum ba kin pynhiar ïa ka metïap jong u na uta u dieng, bad ban bred ïa ka ha khmat ka khyrdop jong kata ka shnong, bad ban kynton ka kynton maw ka bakhraw halor jong ka, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua la tei ka duwan ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ha u lum Ebal,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> kumba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum ïa ki khun Israel, kumba la thoh ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum u Moses, “ka duwan maw tylli, halor jong ki ym shym pyndei nar mano mano ruh:” bad ki la ainguh halor jong ka da ki jingainguh thang ha U Trai, ki la kñia ruh ki jingainguh pynïasuk.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U la thoh ruh hangta ha kita ki maw, ka jingkyllum ka hukum u Moses, ïa kaba u la thoh ha khmat ki khun Israel.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki Israel baroh, bad ki tymmen basan jong ki, ki rangbah synshar jong ki bad ki nongbishar jong ki ruh, ki la ïeng baroh ar liang ïa ka synduk ha khmat ki lyngdoh ki Lebi, kiba bah ïa kata ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, u nongwei ruh kumjuh kum u trai-shnong; shiteng na ki, ki ha ka liang u lum Gerisim, bad shiteng ha ka liang u lum Ebal; kumba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum, ba kin kyrkhu shuwa eh ïa u paidbah Israel.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hadien kata, u la pule ïa ki ktien ka hukum baroh, ïa ki jingkyrkhu bad ïa ki jingtim, katba kum ïa kaba la thoh baroh ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ym shym don kawei ka ktien na kaba u Moses u la hukum baroh, ïa kaba u Joshua um shym la pule ha u paidbah ki Israel, lem bad ki kynthei, bad ki khynnah, bad u nongwei uba ïaid hapdeng jong ki."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba ki syiem baroh kiba ha kane ka liang ka Jordan, ha ki lum, ha ki them, bad ha ki rud ka duriaw bah marpyrshah u Lebanon, ki Hit keiñ bad ki Amor, ki Kanaan, ki Peris, ki Hib, bad ki Jebus, ki la bna;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ynda kumta, ki la lum lang, da kawei ka jingmut, ban ïaleh ïa u Joshua bad ïa ki Israel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba ki nong Gibeon ki la ïohsngew ïa kaba u Joshua u la leh ïa ka Jerikho bad ïa ka Ai,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ki ruh ki la leh sianti, bad ki la leit bad ki la leh mynleh kum ki nonglam-ktien, ki la buh ruh ïa ki byrni rim halor ki kadda jong ki, bad ki lywa snieh Waiñ ki barim ba la pdang bad ba la teh;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ki juti rim bad ba la syrdep ruh ha la ki sla'jat, bad ki jaiñ rim halor jong ki; bad u kpu ka jingbam jong ki baroh ruh u la tyrkhong bad u la bthuh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la leit sha u Joshua ha ka dara ha Gilgal, bad ki la ong ha u, bad ha u paidbah Israel, “Ngi la wan na ka ri kaba jngai: mynta te to ïateh jutang bad ngi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u paidbah Israel u la ong ha ki Hib, “Lehse phi shong hapdeng jong ngi: namar kata, ngin ïateh jutang kumno bad phi?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki la ong ha u Joshua, “Ngi long ki shakri jong me.” Te u Joshua u la ong ha ki, “Phi long kiei? Bad na-ei phi wan?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la ong ha u, “Ki shakri jong me ki la wan na ka ri kaba jngai eh na ka bynta ka kyrteng U Trai uba U Blei jong me: namar ba ngi la ïohsngew ïa ka nam jong u, bad ïa baroh ba u la leh ha Ijipt,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad baroh ba u la leh ïa ar ngut ki syiem ki Amor, kiba sha shiliang ka Jordan, ïa u Sihon u syiem ka Heshbon, bad ïa u Og u syiem ka Bashan, uba ju don ha Ashtaroth.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, ki tymmen basan jong ngi bad ki trai-shnong ka ri jong ngi baroh ki la kren ha ngi, ki da ong, ‘To shim ka jingbam ryngkat bad phi ha lynti, to leit ïashem bad ki, ong ruh ha ki, “Ngi long ki shakri jong phi: namar kata, to ïateh jutang bad ngi.” ’",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ïa une u kpu jong ngi, ngi la shim ban long jingbam ïa ngi haba u dang shit na la ki ïing ha kata ka sngi ba ngi la mih ban wan sha phi; hynrei mynta, ha khmih, u la tyrkhong bad u la bthuh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kine ruh ki lywa snieh Waiñ ba ngi la pyndap haba ki dang thymmai; ha khmih ruh, ki la pdang: ki jaiñ jong ngi ruh bad ki juti jong ngi ki la man rim namar ba jngai eh ka lynti.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kita ki rangbah ki la shim na ka jingbam jong ki, bad kim shym la ïakylli na ka shyntur U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Joshua u la pynlong ka jingïasuk bad ki, bad u la ïateh jutang bad ki, ban ri im ïa ki: ki rangbah jong u paidbah ruh ki la smai ha ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, hadien lai sngi ynda ki la ïateh jutang bad ki, ki la ïohsngew ba ki long ki paramarjan jong ki, bad ba ki shong hapdeng jong ki pynban.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïaleit, bad ki la poi ha ki shnong jong ki ha ka sngi balai. Te ki shnong jong ki, ki la long ka Gibeon, bad Khephirah, bad ka Beeroth, bad ka Kiriath-jearim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki khun Israel kim shym pynïap ïa ki, namar ki rangbah jong ki paidbah ki la smai ha ki da U Trai, U Blei ki Israel. Te u paidbah baroh u la khñium ïa kita ki rangbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ki rangbah baroh ki la ong ha u paidbah baroh, “Ngi la smai ha ki da U Trai, U Blei ki Israel: namar kata, ngim lah ban ktah ïa ki mynta.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ngin leh kumne ïa ki, bad to ai ba kin im; ïoh ba ka jingbitar kan hap halor jong ngi, namar kata ka jingsmai ba ngi la smai ha ki.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki rangbah ki la ong ha ki, “Ai ba kin im:” kumta, ki long ki nongthoh dieng bad ki nongtong um ïa u paidbah baroh; kumba ki rangbah ki la kren ha ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Joshua u la khot ïa ki, bad u la kren ha ki, u da ong, “Balei phi la shukor ïa ngi, phi da ong, ‘Ngi long kiba jngai eh na phi,’ haba phi shong hapdeng jong ngi pynban?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Mynta te phi long kiba la tim, bad uwei na phi un ym lait na ka ban long mraw, ki nongthoh dieng bad ki nongtong um ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ngi.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ha u Joshua, bad ki la ong, “Namar ba la ïathuh shisha ha ki shakri jong me, kumno ba U Trai U Blei jong me u la hukum ïa u Moses u shakri jong u ban ai ha phi ïa ka ri baroh, bad ban pynduh baroh ïa ki trai-shnong jong kata ka ri na khmat jong phi; namar kata, ngi la sheptieng shibun ïa la ka jingim namar jong phi, bad ngi la leh ïa kane.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mynta te, ha khmih, ngi don ha ka kti jong me: kumba me sngewbha bad sngewdei ban leh ïa ngi, to leh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kumta ruh, u la leh ïa ki, bad u la pyllait ïa ki na ka kti ki khun Israel, ba kim shym la pynïap ïa ki,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad u Joshua u la pynlong ïa ki ha kata ka sngi, ki nongthoh dieng bad ki nongtong um ïa u paidbah, bad ïa ka duwan U Trai, haduh kane ka sngi, ha kata ka jaka kaba un jied."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Adonisedek u syiem ka Jerusalem u la ïohsngew kumno u Joshua u la jop ïa ka Ai, bad ba u la pynduh khoit ïa ka; kumba u la leh ïa ka Jerikho bad ïa u syiem jong ka, kumta, u la leh ïa ka Ai bad ïa u syiem jong ka; bad kumno ki nong Gibeon ki la ïasuk bad ki Israel, bad ki la don hapdeng jong ki ruh;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> kumta, ki la sheptieng shibun eh, namar ka Gibeon ka la long ka nongbah ka bakhraw, kum kawei na ki nongbah shong syiem, bad namar ka la long kham khraw ban ïa ka Ai, bad ki rangbah jong ka baroh ruh kiba khlaiñ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata, u Adonisedek u syiem ka Jerusalem u la phah ha u Hoham u syiem ka Hebron, bad ha u Piram u syiem ka Jarmuth, bad ha u Japhia u syiem ka Lakhish, bad ha u Debir u syiem ka Eglon, u da ong,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “To wan kiew sha nga, to ïarap ïa nga ruh, ba ngin ïoh jop ïa ka Gibeon: namar ba ka la ïasuk bad u Joshua bad ki khun Israel.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, kita ki san ngut ki syiem ki Amor, u syiem ka Jerusalem, u syiem ka Hebron, u syiem ka Jarmuth, u syiem ka Lakhish, u syiem ka Eglon, ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la leit kiew, ma ki bad ki paidïapom jong ki baroh, bad ki la shong dara ha khmat ka Gibeon, bad ki la ïaleh ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki nong Gibeon ki la phah ha u Joshua sha ka dara ha Gilgal, ki da ong, “Wat kynran ïa la ka kti na ki shakri jong me; wan kiew kloi sha ngi, to pynim ïa ngi ruh, bad to ïarap ïa ngi: namar ki syiem ki Amor baroh kiba shong ha ri lum ki la ïalum lang pyrshah ïa ngi.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la kiew na Gilgal, ma u bad ki paidïapom baroh ryngkat bad u, bad baroh ki briew ki bashait bashlur.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Wat sheptieng ïa ki: namar nga la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong me; ym don uwei na ki u ban ïeng ha khmat jong me.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, u Joshua u la wan buk ha ki; namar u la kiew artet na Gilgal baroh shi miet.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad U Trai u la pynjot ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel, bad u la pynïap ïa ki da ka jingpynïap bakhraw ha Gibeon, u la beh ïa ki ruh ha ka lynti ka thiep Beth-horon, bad u la pynïap ïa ki haduh Asekah, bad haduh Makkedah.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la jia ruh, katba ki la phet ïap na khmat ki Israel, haba ki la don ha ka jur Beth-horon, ba U Trai u la pynhap ki maw bakhraw halor jong ki na bneng haduh Asekah, bad ki la ïap: ki la long ruh kham bun kiba la ïap da u phria ban ïa kita ba ki khun Israel ki la pynïap da ka waitlam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua u la kren ha U Trai ha kata ka sngi ba U Trai u la aiti noh ïa ki Amor ha khmat ki khun Israel, bad u la ong ha khmat ki Israel, “Ko sngi, to phan ïeng thik ha Gibeon, ma me ruh, ko bnai, ha ka them Aijalon.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka sngi ka la ïeng thik, u bnai ruh u la sangeh, ha ban da u paidbah u la pynhiar kput halor ki nongshun. Ym shym la thoh ïa kane ha Ka Kitab u Jashar? Kumta, ka sngi ka la ïeng thik hapdeng ka bneng, bad kam shym la kyrkieh ban sep kumba shi sngi biang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ym shym don ka sngi kum kata mynshuwa jong ka lane hadien jong ka, ba U Trai u la sngap ïa ka ktien kyrpad u briew: naba U Trai u la ïaleh na ka bynta ki Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Joshua u la leit phai, ma u bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, sha ka dara ha Gilgal.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, kita ki san ngut ki syiem ki la phet ïap, bad ki la ïarieh ha ka krem ha Makkedah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Joshua, da kaba ong, “La shem ïa kita ki san ngut ki syiem, ba ki la ïarieh ha ka krem ha Makkedah.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong, “Pyntyllun ki maw bakhraw ha khmat kata ka krem, buh briew ruh hajan jong ka ban ap ïa ki:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ma phi te wat sangeh; beh ïa la ki nongshun, pynïap ruh ïa ki bakhatduh na ki; wat shah ba kin rung ha ki shnong jong ki: namar U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong phi.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba u Joshua bad ki khun Israel ki la wai ban pynïap ïa ki da ka jingpynïap bakhraw, ha ban da ki la duh noh khoit, bad ba kat kiba sah na ki, ki la rung ha ki nongbah ba la ker kynroh,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> kumta, uta u paidbah baroh u la phai noh sha ka dara ha u Joshua ha Makkedah ha kaba suk: mano mano ruh ym shym la pynkhih ïa la u thylliej pyrshah ïa uwei na ki khun Israel.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua u la ong, “To plie ïa ka khmat ka krem, wallam ruh ïa kita san ngut ki syiem na kata ka krem ha nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la leh kumta, bad ki la wallam ïa kita san ngut ki syiem ha u na kata ka krem, u syiem ka Jerusalem, u syiem ka Hebron, u syiem ka Jarmuth, u syiem ka Lakhish, bad u syiem ka Eglon.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ki la wallam noh ïa kita ki syiem ha u Joshua, u Joshua u la phah khot ïa uta u paidbah Israel baroh, bad u la ong ha ki rangbah ki paidïapom kiba la leit bad u, “Ale hajan, buh ruh ïa la ki poh'jat halor ki ryndang jong kine ki syiem.” Te ki la wan hajan, bad ki la buh ruh ïa la ki poh'jat halor ki ryndang jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong ha ki, “Wat sheptieng, lymne wat kyiuh; pynkhlaiñ ïa lade pynshlur bha ïa lade: naba kumne U Trai un leh ïa ki nongshun jong phi baroh ïa kiba phi ïaleh.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hadien kata, u Joshua u la shoh ïa ki, bad u la pynïap ïa ki, bad u la sdien ïa ki ruh halor san tylli ki dieng: bad ki la sdien halor kita ki dieng haduh janmiet.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ka la jia ruh ha ka por ba ka sngi ka la sep, ba u Joshua u la hukum, bad ki la pynhiar ïa ki na kita ki dieng bad ki la bred ïa ki ha kata ka krem ha kaba ki la ïarieh, bad ki la buh ïa ki maw bakhraw ha khmat kata ka krem, kiba sah haduh kane ka sngi hi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi, u Joshua u la jop ïa ka Makkedah, bad u la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ïa u syiem jong ka; u la pynduh khoit ïa ki bad ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka, um shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh: bad u la leh ïa u syiem ka Makkedah kumba u la leh ïa u syiem ka Jerikho.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, ki la leit na Makkedah sha Libnah, bad u la ïaleh ïa ka Libnah:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Trai u la ai noh ïa ka ruh, bad ïa u syiem jong ka, ha ka kti ki Israel; bad u la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ki mynsiem baroh ruh kiba ha ka; um shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh; bad u la leh ïa u syiem jong ka kumba u la leh ïa u syiem ka Jerikho.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Joshua u la leit na Libnah, bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, sha Lakhish, bad u la ker tawiar ïa ka, bad u la ïaleh ïa ka ruh:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ka Lakhish ha ka kti ki Israel, kiba la jop ïa ka ha ka sngi ka ba-ar, bad ki la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka, katba kum ïa baroh ba u la leh ïa ka Libnah.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ynda kumta, u Horam u syiem ka Geser u la wan kiew ban ïarap ïa ka Lakhish; bad u Joshua u la pom ïa u bad ïa ki briew jong u, haduh ba um shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad na Lakhish, u Joshua u la leit bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u sha Eglon; bad ki la ker tawiar ïa ka, bad ki la ïaleh ïa ka;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad ki la jop ïa ka ruh ha kata ka sngi, bad ki la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka, u la pynduh khoit ha kata ka sngi, katba kum ïa baroh ba u la leh ïa ka Lakhish.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u Joshua u la leit kiew na Eglon bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u sha Hebron; bad ki la ïaleh ïa ka:",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ki la jop ïa ka, bad ki la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad u syiem jong ka, bad ki shnong jong ka baroh, bad ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka; um shym pynsah shuh wat uwei ruh, katba kum ïa baroh ba u la leh ïa ka Eglon; namar u la pynduh khoit ïa ka, bad ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Joshua u la phai noh, bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, sha Debir; bad ki la ïaleh ïa ka:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> u la jop ïa ka ruh bad ïa u syiem jong ka, bad ïa ki shnong jong ka baroh; bad ki la pom ïa ki da ka syrti waitlam, bad u la pynduh khoit ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka; um shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh: kumba u la leh ïa ka Hebron, kumta u la leh ïa ka Debir, bad ïa u syiem jong ka; kumba u la leh ïa ka Libnah ruh, bad ïa u syiem jong ka.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la jop ïa ka ri baroh, ïa ka ri lum, bad ïa ka shathie, bad ïa ka ri them, bad ïa ki ranab lum, bad ïa ki syiem jong ki baroh; um shym la pynsah uwei ruh: hynrei, u la pynduh khoit ïa baroh kat kiba don mynsiem, kumba U Trai U Blei ki Israel, u la hukum.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad u Joshua u la pom ïa ki naduh Kadesh-barnea haduh Gasa, ka ri Goshen baroh ruh, haduh Gibeon.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ïa kine ki syiem baroh bad ka ri jong ki u Joshua u la jop ha kajuh ka por, namar U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u la ïaleh na ka bynta ki Israel.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hadien kata, u Joshua u la leit phai noh, bad ki Israel baroh ryngkat bad u, sha ka dara ha Gilgal."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Jabin u syiem ka Hasor u la ïohsngew ïa kane, u la phah ha u Jobab u syiem ka Madon, bad ha u syiem ka Shimron, bad ha u syiem ka Akhshaph,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ha ki syiem kiba shaphang shatei, ha ri lum bad ha ri madan shaphang shathie na Khinneroth, bad ha ka ri them, bad ha ri lum Dor shaphang sepngi,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ha ki Kanaan shaphang mihngi bad shaphang sepngi, bad ha ki Amor, bad ki Hit, bad ki Peris, bad ki Jebus ha ri lum, bad ha ki Hib harum Hermon ha ri Mispah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la mih noh, ma ki bad baroh ki paidïapom jong ki ryngkat bad ki, shibun ki briew, kat u shyiap uba harud duriaw ha ka jingbun lem bad ki kulai bad ki kali shibun eh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba kine ki syiem baroh ki la ïashem lang, ki la wan shong dara lang ha ki um Merom, ban ïaleh ïa ki Israel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Joshua, “Wat sheptieng namar jong ki: namar lashai hamar kane ka por ngan aiti noh ïa ki baroh ba la pynïap ha khmat ki Israel: men thait ïa ki thied khohwah ki kulai jong ki, bad men thang ïa ki kali jong ki da ka ding.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, u Joshua bad ki paidïapom baroh ryngkat bad u, ki la wan buk ha ki ha ki um Merom, bad ki la kynrup ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Israel, ki te ki la pom ïa ki, bad ki la beh ïa ki haduh ka Sidon bah, bad haduh Misrephoth-maim, bad haduh ka them Mispeh shaphang mihngi; bad ki la pom ïa ki, haduh ba kim shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Joshua u la leh ha ki kat kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u: u la thait ïa ki thied ki khohwah ki kulai jong ki, bad u la thang ïa ki kali jong ki da ka ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Joshua u la phai noh ha kata por, bad u la jop ïa ka Hasor, bad u la pom ïa u syiem jong ka da ka waitlam: namar ka Hasor mynshuwa ka la long ha khlieh kita ki hima baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la pom ïa ki mynsiem baroh kiba ha ka da ka syrti waitlam, ki da pynduh khoit ïa ki: ym shym pynsah shuh kawei ka mynsiem: bad u la thang ïa ka Hasor da ka ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ïa ki shnong jong kita ki syiem baroh, bad ïa ki syiem jong ki baroh ruh, u Joshua u la jop, bad u la pom ïa ki da ka syrti waitlam, bad u la pynduh khoit ïa ki; kumba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita ki shnong kiba don ha la ki lum, ki Israel kim shym thang, tang ïa ka Hasor hi; ïa kata u Joshua u la thang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ïa ka jinglute baroh jong kine ki shnong, bad ïa ki jingri, ki khun Israel ki la shim ban long ka jinglute ïa lade; hynrei, ïa u briew baroh ki la pom da ka syrti waitlam, haduh ba ki la pynduh noh khoit ïa ki, kim shym pynsah shuh kawei ka mynsiem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses u shakri jong u, kumta u Moses u la hukum ïa u Joshua; kumta ruh u Joshua u la leh; um shym iehnoh ei ei khlem da leh na kita baroh ba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la shim ïa kata ka ri baroh, ïa ka ri lum, bad ka ri shaphang shathie, bad ïa ka ri Goshen baroh, bad ïa ka ri them, bad ïa ka ri madan, bad ïa ka ri lum Israel, bad ïa ka ri them jong u de;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> naduh u lum Halak keiñ, uba leit suh sha Seir, haduh Baal-gad ha ka them Lebanon harum u lum Hermon: bad ïa ki syiem jong ki baroh u la kem, bad u la pom ïa ki, bad u la pynïap ïa ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Joshua u la ïaleh thma slem bad kita ki syiem baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ym shym don kawei ka shnong ba la ïasuk bad ki khun Israel, tang ki Hib ki nong Gibeon: ki la jop ïa ki baroh ha ka thma.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar ka la long na U Trai ban pyneh ïa ki dohnud jong ki, ba kin wan ïaleh ïa ki Israel ha ka thma, ba un ïoh pynduh ïa ki khoit, ba kin ym ïoh ka jingisynei, hynrei, ba un pynduh ïa ki, kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ha kata ka por ruh u Joshua u la wan, bad u la pynduh ïa ki Anak na ka ri lum, na Hebron, na Debir, na Anab, bad na ka ri lum Judah baroh, bad na ka ri lum Israel baroh: u Joshua u la pynduh khoit ïa ki bad ïa ki shnong jong ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ym shym pynsah shuh uwei ruh na ki Anak ha ka ri ki khun Israel: tang ha Gasa, ha Gath, bad ha Ashdod, ki dang sah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la shim ïa kata ka ri baroh, kat kumba U Trai u la ong ha u Moses baroh; bad u Joshua u la ai kynti ïa ka ha ki Israel katba kum ki bynta jong ki ha la ki jaid ki jaid. Bad ka ri ka la shongthait na ka thma."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki syiem jong kata ka ri, kiba ki khun Israel ki la jop, bad ki la ïoh ïa ka ri jong ki sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi, naduh ka them Arnon haduh u lum Hermon, bad ka ri madan baroh shaphang mihngi:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> U Sihon u syiem ki Amor, uba ju shong ha Heshbon, bad uba synshar naduh Aroer, kaba ha ka rud ka them Arnon, bad naduh pdeng kata ka them, bad na shiteng ka Gilead, haduh ka wah Jabbok, kaba long ka pud ki khun u Ammon;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad naduh ka ri madan haduh ka duriaw Khinneroth, shaphang mihngi, bad haduh ka duriaw ka madan, ka Duriaw Mluh keiñ, shaphang mihngi, ka lynti sha Beth-jeshimoth; bad shaphang shathie, harum ki ranab Piskah:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ka pud u Og u syiem ka Bashan, uba dang sah na ki riewradbah, uba ju shong ha Ashtaroth bad ha Edrei,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad u la synshar ha u lum Hermon, bad ha Salekah, bad ha Bashan baroh, haduh ka pud ki Geshur bad ki Maakath, bad shiteng ka Gilead, ka pud u Sihon u syiem ka Heshbon.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ïa kita, u Moses u shakri U Trai bad ki khun Israel, ki la jop: bad u Moses u shakri U Trai u la ai ïa ka ban long ka bynta ïa ki Reuben, bad ki Gad, bad ki shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad kine ki long ki syiem jong kata ka ri kaba u Joshua bad ki khun Israel ki la jop, ha kane ka liang ka Jordan shaphang sepngi, naduh Baal-gad ha ka them Lebanon haduh u lum Halak, uba leit suh sha Seir; bad u Joshua u la ai ïa ka ha ki jaid Israel ban long ka bynta kat kum ki bynta jong ki;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ha ri lum, bad ha ri them, bad ha ri madan, bad ha ki ranab, bad ha ka ri khlaw, bad ha ka ri shathie; ki Hit, ki Amor, bad ki Kanaan, ki Peris, ki Hib, bad ki Jebus:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> u syiem ka Jerikho, uwei; u syiem ka Ai, kaba hajan Bethel, uwei;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u syiem ka Jerusalem, uwei; u syiem ka Hebron, uwei;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> u syiem ka Jarmuth, uwei; u syiem ka Lakhish, uwei;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> u syiem ka Eglon, uwei; u syiem ka Geser, uwei;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> u syiem ka Debir, uwei; u syiem ka Geder, uwei;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u syiem ka Hormah, uwei; u syiem ka Arad, uwei;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> u syiem ka Libnah, uwei; u syiem ka Adullam, uwei;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> u syiem ka Makkedah, uwei; u syiem ka Bethel, uwei;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> u syiem ka Tappuah, uwei; u syiem ka Hepher, uwei;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> u syiem ka Aphek, uwei; u syiem ka Lasharon, uwei;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> u syiem ka Madon, uwei; u syiem ka Hasor, uwei;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> u syiem ka Shimron-meron, uwei; u syiem ka Akhshaph, uwei;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> u syiem ka Taanakh, uwei; u syiem ka Megiddo, uwei;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> u syiem ka Kedesh, uwei, u syiem ka Jokneam ha Karmel, uwei;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> u syiem ka Dor ha ri Dor, uwei; u syiem ki Goiim ha Gilgal, uwei;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u syiem ka Tirsah, uwei: ki syiem baroh laiphew wei."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Joshua u la tymmen bad u la hiar arsut ka rta; bad U Trai u la ong ha u, “Me la tymmen bad me la hiar arsut ka rta, hynrei, dang sah bun ka khyndew kaba dei ban ïoh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kane ka long ka khyndew kaba dang sah: ki phang ki Philistia baroh, bad ki Geshur baroh;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na Shihor, kaba ha shuwa ka Ijipt, haduh ka pud ka Ekron shaphang shatei, ïa kata, la ñiew ka jong ki Kanaan: san ngut ki doloi ki Philistia; ki Gasa, ki Ashdod, ki Ashkelon, ki Gath, bad ki Ekron; ki Abbim ruh, shaphang shathie:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ka ri ki Kanaan baroh, bad ka Mearah ka jong ki Sidon, haduh Aphek, haduh ki pud ki Amor:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ka ri ki Gebal, bad u Lebanon baroh, shaphang kaba mih ka sngi, haduh Baal-gad harum u lum Hermon haduh kaba leit rung sha Hamath:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> kiba shong ha ri lum baroh naduh Lebanon haduh Misrephoth-maim, ki Sidon baroh keiñ: ïa kita, ngan beh na khmat ki khun Israel: tang ba men ïasam ïa ka da ka jingkhalai ha ki Israel ban long ka ri kynti, kumba nga la hukum ïa me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, to ïasam ïa kane ka ri ban long ka ri kynti ha ki khyndai jaid, bad ha shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Lem bad u, ki Reuben bad ki Gad ki la ïoh ïa la ka ri kynti, kaba u Moses u la ai ha ki, sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi, kumba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la ai ha ki;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> naduh Aroer, kaba long ha ka rud ka them Arnon, bad kata ka shnong kaba hapdeng kata ka them, bad ka madan Medeba baroh haduh Dibon;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad baroh ki shnong u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, uba ju synshar ha Heshbon, haduh ka pud ki khun u Ammon;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ka Gilead, bad ka pud ki Geshur bad ki Maakath, bad u lum Hermon baroh, bad ka Bashan baroh haduh Salekah;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ka hima u Og baroh ha Bashan, uba ju synshar ha Ashtaroth bad ha Edrei, (uba sah na ki riewradbah); namar ïa kine u Moses u la pom, bad u la beh noh ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Pynban, ki khun Israel kim shym beh ïa ki Geshur, lymne ki Maakath; hynrei, ki Geshur bad ki Maakath ki la shong hapdeng ki Israel, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Tang ïa ka jaid u Lebi um shym ai ri kynti; ki jingkñia U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ba la pynlong da ka ding, ki long ka jingïoh kynti jong ki, kumba u la ong ha ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Moses u la ai ha ka jaid ki khun u Reuben katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long na Aroer, kaba don ha ka rud ka them Arnon, bad kata ka shnong kaba hapdeng kata ka them; bad ka ri madan baroh hajan Medeba;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ka Heshbon, bad ki shnong jong ka baroh kiba ha ka madan; ka Dibon, bad ka Bamoth-Baal, bad ka Beth-baal-meon;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ka Jahas, bad ka Kedemoth, bad ka Mephaath;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ka Kiriathaim, bad ka Sibmah, bad ka Sereth-shahar ha u lum ka them;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ka Beth-peor, bad ki ranab Piskah, bad ka Beth-jeshimoth;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ki shnong ka ri madan baroh, bad baroh ka hima u Sihon u syiem ki Amor, uba ju synshar ha Heshbon, ïa uba u Moses u la jop lem bad ki rangbah Midian, u Ebi, bad u Rekem, bad u Sur, bad u Hur, bad u Reba, ki rangbah u Sihon, kiba shong ha kata ka ri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ïa u Balaam ruh u khun u Beor, u nongkren byrtong, ki khun Israel ki la pynïap da ka waitlam hapdeng kita kiba ki la pynïap.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ka pud ki khun u Reuben ka la long ka Jordan, bad ka rud jong ka. Kane ka la long ka ri kynti ki khun u Reuben katba kum ki ïing jong ki, ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Moses u la ai ha ka jaid u Gad, ha ki khun u Gad keiñ, katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long ka Jaser, bad ki shnong ka Gilead baroh, bad shiteng ka ri ki khun u Ammon, haduh Aroer kaba ha shuwa Rabbah;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad naduh Heshbon haduh Ramath-mispeh, bad Betonim; bad naduh Mahanaim haduh ka pud ka Debir;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ha ka ri them, ka Beth-haram, bad ka Beth-nimrah, bad ka Sukkoth, bad ka Saphon, kaba sah na ka hima u Sihon u syiem ka Heshbon, ka Jordan bad ka rud jong ka, haduh ka rud ka duriaw Khinneroth sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kane ka long ka ri kynti ki khun u Gad kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Moses u la ai ha ki shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh: bad ka la long ïa ki shiteng jaid ki khun u Manasseh kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long na Mahanaim, ka Bashan baroh, ka hima u Og u syiem ka Bashan baroh, bad baroh ki shnong u Jair, kiba ha Bashan, hynriewphew shnong:",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad shiteng ka Gilead, bad ka Ashtaroth, bad ka Edrei, ki shnong ka hima u Og ha Bashan, ki la dei ïa ki khun u Makhir u khun u Manasseh, ha ki shiteng ki khun u Makhir keiñ kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kine ki long kita ki ri kynti kiba u Moses u la ïasam ha ki madan Moab, sha shiliang ka Jordan hajan Jerikho, shaphang mihngi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, ha ka jaid u Lebi, u Moses um shym ai ri kynti: U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u long ka jingïoh kynti jong ki, kumba u la ong ha ki."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long kita ki ri kynti kiba ki khun Israel ki la ïoh ha ri Kanaan, ïa kiba u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun, bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa na ki jaid ki khun Israel, ki la ïasam ha ki,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> da ka jingkhalai ka jingïoh kynti jong ki, kumba U Trai u la hukum da ka kti u Moses, ha kita ki khyndai jaid, bad ha kata ka shiteng jaid.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba u Moses u la lah ai ka ri kynti jong kita ki ar jaid shiteng ha kata kawei ka liang ka Jordan: hynrei, ha ki Lebi um shym ai ri kynti hapdeng jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Naba ki khun u Joseph ki la long ar jaid, u Manasseh bad u Ephraim: namar kata, kim shym ai bynta ha ki Lebi ha kata ka ri, tang ki nongbah ban shong, bad ki rudnong jong ki na ka bynta ki jingri jong ki bad na ka bynta ka kamai jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumba U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses, kumta ki khun Israel ki la leh, bad ki la ïabynta ïa ka ri.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun u Judah ki la wan ha u Joshua ha Gilgal: bad u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh u nong Kenis u la ong ha u, “Me tip ïa kaba la ong U Trai ha u Moses u briew jong U Blei shaphang jong nga bad shaphang jong me ha Kadesh-barnea.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nga la sawphew snem ka rta mynba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la phah ïa nga na Kadesh-barnea ban khmih syntiat ïa ka ri; bad nga la wallam ktien pat ha u kumba ka la don ha ka dohnud jong nga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Pynban, ki paralok jong nga kiba la leit ryngkat bad nga, ki la pynum ïa ka dohnud u paidbah: hynrei, nga la bud naduh haduh ïa U Trai U Blei jong nga.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Moses u la smai ha kata ka sngi, u da ong, ‘Da shisha kata ka khyndew halor kaba ki sla'jat jong me ki la ïuh, kan long ka ri kynti jong me bad ki khun jong me junom, naba me la bud naduh haduh ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong nga.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mynta te, ha khmih, U Trai u la ri im ïa nga, kumba u la ong, kine sawphew san snem, naduh ba U Trai u la kren ïa kane ka ktien ha u Moses keiñ, mynba ki Israel ki la ïaid ha ka ri khlaw: mynta te, ha khmih, nga long phraphew san snem, ha kane ka sngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Toi ha kane ka sngi, nga dang khlaiñ kumjuh kumba ha kata ka sngi ba u Moses u la phah ïa nga: kumba ka bor jong nga ka la long mynkata, kumta ka bor jong nga ka long mynta ruh, ban ïapom, ban mih shabar bad ban wan shapoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mynta namar kata, to ai ha nga ïa une u lum, shaphang uba u la kren U Trai, myn ha kata ka sngi; namar me la ïohsngew ha kata ka sngi kumno ba ki Anak ki la don hangta, bad ba ki nongbah kiba khraw bad ba la ker kynroh: toi U Trai un don ryngkat bad nga, ba ngan beh noh ïa ki, kumba U Trai u la ong.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Joshua u la kyrkhu ïa u; bad u la ai ïa ka Hebron ha u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh ban long ka ri kynti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, ka Hebron ka la long ka ri kynti u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh u nong Kenis, haduh kane ka sngi; namar ba u la bud naduh haduh ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ka kyrteng ka Hebron mynshuwa ka la long “ka Kiriath-arba;” uta u Arba u la long u briew u bakhraw tam hapdeng ki Anak. Bad ka ri ka la ïoh ka jingshongthait na ka thma."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka bynta ka jaid ki khun u Judah katba kum ki ïing jong ki ka la long haduh ka pud ka Edom, jin haduh ka ri khlaw Sin shaphang shathie, ha ka bakut shaphang shathie.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki shaphang shathie ka la long naduh ka bakut ka Duriaw Mluh, naduh ka khmut kaba phai shaphang shathie:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ka la lam shaphang shathie na ka thiep Akrabbim bad ka la pom shaduh Sin, bad ka la kiew na shaphang shathie jong ka Kadesh-barnea, bad ka la poi hajan Hesron, bad ka la kiew sha Adar, bad ka la leit sawdong haduh Karka:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ka la leit haduh Asmon, bad ka la leit mih haduh ka wah Ijipt; bad ki bakut kata ka pud ki la long harud ka duriaw: kane kan long ka pud jong phi shaphang shathie.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka pud shaphang mihngi ka la long ka Duriaw Mluh, haduh ka bakut ka Jordan. Bad ka pud shaphang shatei ka la long naduh ka khmut ka duriaw ha ka bakut ka Jordan:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad kane ka pud ka la leit kiew sha Beth-hoglah, bad ka la leit shaphang shatei jong ka Beth-arabah; bad kane ka pud ka la leit kiew sha u maw jong u Bohan u khun u Reuben:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ka pud ka la kiew artet sha Debir na ka them Akhor, bad kumta shatei, da phai shaphang Gilgal, kata ka long marpyrshah u thiep Adummim, uba long shaphang shathie na ka wah: kata ka pud ka la pom shaphang ki um En-shemesh, bad ka bakut jong ka, ka la long ha En-rogel:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ka pud ka la kiew artet ïa ka them u khun u Hinnom ha ka liang kaba shaphang shathie ki Jebus (kata ka long “ka Jerusalem”): bad ka pud ka la leit kiew sha kliar uta u lum uba ha khmat ka them Hinnom shaphang sepngi, kaba don ha ka bakut ka them Rephaim shaphang shatei:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ka pud ka la siat na kliar uta u lum haduh ka umpohliew Nephtoah, bad ka la mih ha ki shnong u lum Ephron; bad ka pud ka la siat sha Baalah (kaba long “ka Kiriath-jearim”):",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ka pud ka la ïaid tawiar na Baalah shaphang sepngi shaduh u lum Seir, bad ka la pom haduh trai u lum Jearim shaphang shatei (kata ka long “ka Khesalon”), bad ka la hiar sha Beth-shemesh, bad ka la suh sha Timnah:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad kata ka pud ka la siat sha khap ka Ekron shaphang shatei: bad ka pud ka la leit sha Shikkeron, bad ka la pom sha u lum Baalah, bad ka la poi sha Jabnil; bad ki kut ka pud ki ha ka duriaw.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka pud shaphang sepngi ka la long ka duriaw bah, bad ka rud jong ka. Kane ka long ka pud ki khun u Judah baroh sawdong kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ïa u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh u la ai ka bynta hapdeng ki khun u Judah, katba kum ka hukum U Trai ha u Joshua, ka shnong u Arba u kpa u Anak keiñ, (kata ka long “ka Hebron”).",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Kaleb u la beh nangta ïa ki lai ngut ki khun u Anak, u Sheshai, u Ahiman, bad u Talmai, ki khun u Anak.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u la leit kiew nangta pyrshah ïa ki nong Debir: te ka kyrteng ka Debir mynshuwa ka la long “ka Kiriath-sepher.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Kaleb u la ong, “Jar uba pom ïa ka Kiriath-sepher, bad uba jop ïa ka, ha uta ngan buh kurim ïa ka Akhsah ka khun jong nga.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Othniel u khun u Kenas, u para u Kaleb, u la jop ïa ka: te u la buh kurim bad u, ïa ka Akhsah ka khun jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka la jia, haba ka la wan ha u, ka la kyntu ïa u ban pan ka lyngkha na u kpa jong ka: bad ka la hiar nalor ka kadda jong ka; te u Kaleb u la ong ha ka, “Pha kwah aïu?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ka la ïathuh, “Ai ha nga ka jingkyrkhu; namar ba me la ai ha nga ka khyndew shaphang shathie, to ai ruh ha nga ki umpohliew.” Bad u la ai ha ka, ïa kita ki umpohliew kiba haneng bad kita ki umpohliew kiba harum.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kane ka long ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Judah kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki shnong ki bakut ka jaid ki khun u Judah shaphang ka pud ka Edom shaphang shathie ki la long ka Kabsil, bad ka Eder, bad ka Jagur;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ka Kinah, bad ka Dimonah, bad ka Adadah;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad ka Kedesh, bad ka Hasor bad ka Ithnan;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ka Siph, bad ka Telem, bad ka Bealoth:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad ka Hasor-hadattah, bad ka Kerioth-hesron, (kata ka long “ka Hasor”);",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ka Amam, bad ka Shema, bad ka Moladah;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ka Hasar-gaddah, bad ka Heshmon, bad ka Beth-pelet;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ka Hasar-shual, bad ka Beer-sheba, bad ka Bisiothiah;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ka Baalah, bad ka Iyim, bad ka Esem;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ka Eltolad, bad ka Khesil, bad ka Hormah;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ka Siklag, bad ka Madmannah, bad ka Sansannah;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> bad ka Lebaoth, bad ka Shilhim, bad ka Ain, bad ka Rimmon: baroh ki nongbah ki long arphew khyndai tylli, bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ha ka ri them, ka Eshtaol, bad ka Sorah, bad ka Ashnah;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad ka Sanoah, bad ka En-gannim, ka Tappuah, bad ka Enam;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ka Jarmuth, bad ka Adullam, ka Sokoh, bad ka Asekah;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad ka Sharaim, bad ka Adithaim, bad ka Gederah, bad ka Gederothaim; khatsaw ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ka Senan, bad ka Hadashah, bad ka Migdal-gad;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ka Dilean, bad ka Mispeh, bad ka Jokthil;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ka Lakhish, bad ka Boskath, bad ka Eglon;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> bad ka Kabbon, bad ka Lahmam, bad ka Khitlish;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> bad ka Gederoth, ka Beth-dagon, bad ka Naamah, bad ka Makkedah; khathynriew ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ka Libnah, bad ka Ether, bad ka Ashan;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad ka Iphtah, bad ka Ashnah, bad ka Nesib;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad ka Keilah, bad ka Akhsib, bad ka Mareshah; khyndai ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ka Ekron, lem bad ki nongbah jong ka bad ki nongrit jong ka:",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> naduh Ekron haduh ka duriaw, baroh kiba hajan Ashdod, bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Ka Ashdod, lem bad ki nongbah jong ka bad ki nongrit jong ka; ka Gasa, lem bad ki nongbah jong ka bad ki nongrit jong ka; haduh ka wah Ijipt, bad ka duriaw bah, bad ka rud jong ka.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad ha ri lum, ka Shamir, bad ka Jattir, bad ka Sokoh;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> bad ka Dannah, bad ka Kiriath-sannah (kata ka long “ka Debir”);",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad ka Anab, bad ka Eshtemoh, bad ka Anim;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> bad ka Goshen, bad ka Holon, bad ka Giloh; khatwei ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Ka Arab, bad ka Dumah, bad ka Eshean;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> bad ka Janum, bad ka Beth-tappuah, bad ka Aphekah;",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> bad ka Humtah, bad ka Kiriath-arba (kata ka long “ka Hebron”), bad ka Sior; khyndai ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Ka Maon, ka Karmel, bad ka Siph, bad ka Juttah;",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> bad ka Jesril, bad ka Jokdeam, bad ka Sanoah;",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> ka Kain, ka Gibeah, bad ka Timnah; shiphew ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Ka Halhul, ka Beth-sur, bad ka Gedor;",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> ka Maarath, bad ka Beth-anoth bad ka Eltekon, hynriew ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Ka Kiriath-baal (kata ka long “ka Kiriath-jearim”), bad ka Rabbah; ar tylli ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ha ka ri khlaw, ka Beth-arabah, ka Middin, bad ka Sekakah;",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> bad ka Nibshan, bad ka Nongbah ka Mluh, bad ka En-gedi; hynriew ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Hynrei, ki khun u Judah kim shym lah ban beh ïa ki Jebus, kiba shong ha Jerusalem: hynrei, ki Jebus ki shong ryngkat bad ki khun u Judah ha Jerusalem, haduh kane ka sngi."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka bynta ïa ki khun u Joseph ka la suh naduh ka Jordan hajan ka Jerikho, ha ki um Jerikho shaphang mihngi, kata ka ri khlaw, ka da kiew artet na Jerikho lyngba ka ri lum sha Bethel;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ka la suh na Bethel sha Lus, bad ka la pom haduh ki pud ki Arkhi sha Ataroth;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ka la hiar shaphang sepngi sha ki phang ki Japhlet sha khap ka Beth-horon kaba harum, bad haduh ka Geser; bad ki bakut jong ka ki la don ha ka duriaw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, ki khun u Joseph, u Manasseh bad u Ephraim, ki la shim ïa la ka ri kynti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka pud ki khun u Ephraim kat kum ka ïing jong ki ka la long kumne: ka pud ka ri kynti jong ki shaphang mihngi ka la long ka Ataroth-addar, haduh Beth-horon kaba shaneng;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ka pud ka la leit shaphang ka duriaw sha Mikhmethah shaphang shatei; bad kata ka pud ka la phai tawiar shaphang mihngi sha Taanath-sheiloh, bad ka la leit lait shaphang mihngi jong ka Janoah;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad ka la hiar na Janoah sha Ataroth, bad sha Naarah, bad ka la poi sha Jerikho, bad ka la leit mih ha Jordan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Tappuah ka pud ka la leit shaphang sepngi haduh ka wah Kanah; bad ki bakut jong ka ki la don ha ka duriaw. Kane ka long ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Ephraim kat kum ki ïing jong ki;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> lem bad kita ki nongbah ba la pynkyrpang ïa ki khun u Ephraim hapdeng ka ri kynti ki khun u Manasseh, ki nongbah baroh bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kim shym beh noh ïa ki Kanaan kiba shong ha Geser: hynrei, ki Kanaan ki shong hapdeng ki Ephraim, haduh kane ka sngi, bad ki la long shakri ba ai khajna."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kane ka la long ka bynta ïa ka jaid u Manasseh; namar u la long u khun nyngkong u Joseph. Te u Makhir, u khun nyngkong u Manasseh u kpa u Gilead, namar ba u la long u riewïapom, u la ïoh ïa ka Gilead bad ïa ka Bashan.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kata ka bynta ka la long ïa kiba dang sah na ki khun u Manasseh, kat kum ki ïing jong ki; ïa ki khun u Abieser, bad ïa ki khun u Helek, bad ïa ki khun u Asriel, bad ïa ki khun u Shekhem, bad ïa ki khun u Hepher, bad ïa ki khun u Shemida; kine ki la long ki khun shynrang u Manasseh u khun u Joseph katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Selophehad, u khun u Hepher, u khun u Gilead, u khun u Makhir, u khun u Manasseh, um don khun shynrang, tang ki khun kynthei: bad kine ki kyrteng ki khun kynthei jong u, “ka Mahlah”, bad “ka Noah”, “ka Hoglah”, “ka Milkah”, bad “ka Tirsah”.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la wan hajan ha khmat u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha khmat u Joshua, u khun u Nun, bad ha khmat kita ki rangbah, ki ïa-ong, “U Trai u la hukum ïa u Moses ban ai ïa ngi ka ri kynti hapdeng ki para jong ngi:” namar kata, katba kum ka hukum U Trai u la ai ïa ki ka ri kynti hapdeng ki para u kpa jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka la hap ha u Manasseh shiphew bynta, nalor ka ri Gilead bad ka Bashan, kiba sha shiliang ka Jordan;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> namar ki khun kynthei u Manasseh ki la ïoh ri kynti hapdeng ki khun shynrang jong u: bad kita kiwei ki khun shynrang u Manasseh ki la ïoh ïa ka ri Gilead.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka pud u Manasseh ka la long na Asher sha Mikhmethah, kaba marpyrshah ïa ka Shekhem; bad ka pud ka la leit shaphang kamon shaduh ki nong En-tappuah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Manasseh u la ïoh ïa ka ri Tappuah: hynrei, ka Tappuah hi ha ka pud u Manasseh ka la dei ïa ki khun u Ephraim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ka pud ka la hiar sha ka wah Kanah, shaphang shathie jong kata ka wah; kine ki nongbah ki la dei ki jong u Ephraim hapdeng ki nongbah u Manasseh: bad ka pud u Manasseh ruh ka la long shaphang shatei jong kata ka wah, bad ki bakut jong ka ki la long ha ka duriaw:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> shaphang shathie ka la dei ka jong u Ephraim, bad shaphang shatei ka la dei ka jong u Manasseh, bad ka duriaw ka la long ka pud jong u; bad ki la ïakynduh ha ka jong u Asher shaphang shatei, bad ha ka jong u Issakhar shaphang mihngi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Manasseh u la don ha ka jong u Issakhar bad ha ka jong u Asher, ka Beth-shean bad ki shnong jong ka, ka Ibleam bad ki shnong jong ka, bad kiba shong ha Dor bad ki shnong jong ka, bad kiba shong ha Endor bad ki shnong jong ka, bad kiba shong ha Taanakh bad ki shnong jong ka, bad kiba shong ha Megiddo bad ki shnong jong ka, lai tylli ki jaka keiñ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ki khun u Manasseh kim lah ban beh noh ïa kita kiba shong ha kita ki shnong; hynrei, ki Kanaan ki shu shong bor ha kata ka ri.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Pynban, ynda ki khun Israel ki la nang khraw bor, ki la pynsiew khajna ïa ki Kanaan, hynrei, kim shym beh lut phar ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki khun u Joseph ki la ïakren ha u Joshua, ki ïa-ong, “Balei me la ai ha nga tang kawei ka jingkhalai bad kawei ka bynta ban long ri kynti, haba nga long uba bun briew ruh, namar U Trai u la kyrkhu ïa nga haduh mynta?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Joshua u la ïathuh ha ki, “Lada me long uba bun briew, to leit kiew sha kata ka ri khlaw, bad shyrti ïa me hangta ha ka ri ki Peris bad ki Rephaim; haba u lum Ephraim u khim eh ïa me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki khun u Joseph ki la ong, “Ka ri lum kam biang ïa ngi: bad ki Kanaan baroh kiba shong ha ka ri them ki don ki kali nar, kita kiba don ha Beth-shean bad ki shnong jong ka, bad kiba ha ka them Jesril ruh.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Joshua u la kren ha ka ïing u Joseph, ha u Ephraim bad u Manasseh, u da ong, “Me long uba bun briew, bad me don ka bor bakhraw ruh: men ym ïoh tang kawei ka bynta:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> hynrei, kata ka lum kan long ka jong me; namar la ka long khlaw, men shyrti ïa ka, bad ki pud jong ka kin long ki jong me: namar men beh noh ïa ki Kanaan, la ki don ki kali nar, bad la ki long ki bakhrawbor ruh.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u paidbah ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang ha Sheiloh, bad ki la pynïeng ïa Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng hangta: bad la lah jop ïa ka ri ha shuwa jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad la dang sah hynñiew jaid hapdeng ki khun Israel, ki bym pat ïoh ïa la ka ri kynti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha ki khun Israel, “Haduh katno phin pynslem ban leit ïoh ïa kata ka ri, ïa kaba U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi, u la ai ha phi?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> To sei napdeng jong phi lai ngut ki briew na kawei kawei ka jaid: bad ngan phah ïa ki, bad kin mih, bad kin ïaid ïa kata ka ri, kin jurib ïa ka kat kum ka ri kynti jong ki; bad kin wan pat sha nga.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kin ïasam hynñiew bynta ïa ka: u Judah un sah ha la ka pud shaphang shathie, bad ka ïing u Joseph kan sah ha la ka pud shaphang shatei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad phin jurib ïa kata ka ri hynñiew bynta, bad phin wallam shane ha nga: bad ngan pynkhalai na ka bynta jong phi hangne ha khmat U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naba ki Lebi kim don bynta hapdeng jong phi; namar ka jinglong lyngdoh U Trai ka long ka jingïoh kynti jong ki: bad u Gad bad u Reuben bad shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh ki la ïoh ïa la ka ri kynti sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi, ïa kaba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la ai ha ki.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki la ïaïeng, bad ki la ïaleit: bad u Joshua u la hukum ïa kita kiba leit jurib ïa ka ri, u da ong, “Khie leit ïaid ïa ka ri baroh, bad jurib ïa ka, bad wan pat sha nga, bad ngan pynkhalai na ka bynta jong phi hangne ha khmat U Trai ha Sheiloh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la leit bad ki la ïaid ïa kata ka ri, bad ki la jurib ïa ka katba kum ki shnong, hynñiew bynta ha ka kot, bad ki la wan pat ha u Joshua ha ka dara ha Sheiloh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Joshua u la pynkhalai na ka bynta jong ki ha Sheiloh ha khmat U Trai: bad u la ïasam ïa ka ri ha ki khun Israel katba kum ki bynta jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ka bynta ka jaid ki khun u Benjamin ka la hap kat kum ki ïing jong ki bad ka pud ka bynta jong ki ka la hap hapdeng ki khun u Judah bad ki khun u Joseph.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki shaphang shatei ka la long na ka Jordan; bad ka pud ka la kiew harud Jerikho shaphang shatei, bad ka la kiew sha ka ri lum shaphang sepngi; bad ki bakut jong ka ki la long ha ka ri khlaw Beth-aben.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka pud ka la pom nangta sha Lus, harud Lus keiñ (kata ka long “ka Bethel”), shaphang shathie; bad ka pud ka la hiar sha Ataroth-addar, hajan uta u lum uba shaphang shathie jong ka Beth-horon kaba harum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka pud ka la suh nangta bad ka la ïaid tawiar na ka phang sepngi shathie, na uta u lum uba ha pyrshah Beth-horon shaphang shathie; bad ki bakut jong ka ki la long ha Kiriath-baal (kata ka long “ka Kiriath-jearim”), ka nongbah ki khun u Judah: kane ka long ka pud shaphang sepngi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad kata ka phang shathie ka la long na ka bakut ka Kiriath-jearim, bad ka pud ka la leit mih shaphang sepngi, bad ka la mih ha ka pukri ki um Nephtoah:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ka pud ka la hiar sha ka bakut uta u lum uba ha pyrshah ka them u khun u Hinnom, kaba ha ka them ki Rephaim shaphang shatei; bad ka la hiar sha ka them u Hinnom, markhap ki Jebus shaphang shathie, bad ka la hiar sha En-rogel;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ka la suh na shaphang shatei, bad ka la leit sha En-shemesh, bad ka la leit poi sha Geliloth, kaba ha marpyrshah ka thiep Adummim; bad ka la hiar ha u maw u Bohan u khun u Reuben;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ka la pom sha ka phang ha pyrshah ka Arabah shaphang shatei; bad ka la hiar haduh Arabah:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ka pud ka la pom harud ka Beth-hoglah shaphang shatei: bad ki bakut jong ka pud ki la don ha ka khmut kaba shaphang shatei ka Duriaw Mluh, ha ka bakut ka Jordan shaphang shathie: kane ka pud shaphang shathie.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ka Jordan ka la long ka pud jong ka shaphang mihngi. Kane ka ri kynti ki khun u Benjamin, da ki pud jong ka sawdong, katba kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki nongbah ka jaid ki khun u Benjamin kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki la long ka Jerikho, bad ka Beth-hoglah, bad ka Emek-kesis;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ka Beth-arabah, bad ka Semaraim, bad ka Bethel;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad ka Abbim, bad ka Parah, bad ka Ophrah;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad ka Khephar-ammoni, bad ka Ophni, bad ka Geba; khat-ar ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ka Gibeon, bad ka Ramah, bad ka Beeroth;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ka Mispeh, bad ka Khephirah, bad ka Mosah;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ka Rekem, bad ka Irpil, bad ka Taralah;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ka Selah, ka Eleph, bad ka Jebus (kata ka long “ka Jerusalem”), ka Gibeah, bad ka Kiriath; khatsaw ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de. Kane ka long ka ri kynti ki khun u Benjamin kat kum ki ïing jong ki."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka ba-ar ka la hap ha u Simeon, ha ka jaid ki khun u Simeon keiñ kat kum ki ïing jong ki: bad ka bynta jong ki ka la long ha ka ri kynti ki khun u Judah.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki la ïoh ban long ka ri kynti jong ki, ïa ka Beer-sheba, lane ka Sheba, bad ka Moladah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad ka Hasar-shual, bad ka Balah, bad ka Esem;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ka Eltolad, bad ka Bethul, bad ka Hormah;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ka Siklag, bad ka Beth-markaboth, bad ka Hasar-susah:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad ka Beth-lebaoth, bad ka Sharuhen: khatlai ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ka Ain, ka Rimmon, bad ka Ether, bad ka Ashan; saw tylli ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ki nongrit baroh kiba la don sawdong ïa kine ki nongbah haduh Baalath-beer, ka Ramah kaba shathie. Kane ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Simeon kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ka bynta jong ki khun u Judah ka la long ka ri kynti ki khun u Simeon: namar ka bynta ki khun u Judah ka la bun eh ïa ki: namar kata, ki khun u Simeon ki la ïoh ïa la ka ri kynti ha ka ri kynti jong ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka balai ka la hap ha ki khun u Sabulon kat kum ki ïing jong ki: bad ka pud ka ri kynti jong ki ka la kot haduh Sarid:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ka pud jong ki ka la kiew sha sepngi, haduh Maralah, bad ka la poi haduh Dabbasheth; bad ka la poi haduh ka wah kaba ha pyrshah ka Jokneam;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ka la phai na Sarid shaphang mihngi sha kaba mih ka sngi haduh ka pud ka Khisloth-tabor; bad hadien kata, ka la suh sha Daberath, bad ka la kiew sha Japhia;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad nangta ka la pom shaphang mihngi sha Gath-hepher, sha Eth-kasin; bad ka la suh sha Rimmon kaba kot sha Neah;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ka pud ka la ïaid tawiar ïa ka shaphang shatei, sha Hannathon: bad ki bakut jong ka ki long ha ka them Iphtahel:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ka Kattath, bad ka Nahalal, bad ka Shimron, bad ka Idalah, bad ka Bethlehem: khat-ar ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> kane ka long ka bynta ki khun u Sabulon kat kum ki ïing jong ki, kine ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka jingkhalai ka basaw ka la hap ha u Issakhar, ha ki khun u Issakhar kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long haduh Jesril, bad ka Khesulloth, bad ka Shunem;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ka Hapharaim, bad ka Shion, bad ka Anaharath;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ka Rabbith, bad ka Kishion, bad ka Ebes;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ka Remeth, bad ka En-gannim, bad ka En-haddah, bad ka Beth-passes;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ka pud ka la poi haduh Tabor, bad Shahasumah, bad Beth-shemesh; bad ki bakut ka pud jong ki, ki la long ha Jordan: khathynriew ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kane ka long ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Issakhar kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka basan ka la hap ha ka jaid ki khun u Asher kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long ka Helkath, bad ka Hali, bad ka Beten, bad ka Akhshaph;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad ka Allammelekh, bad ka Amad, bad ka Mishal; bad ka poi sha Karmel shaphang sepngi bad sha Shihor-libnath;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad ka la phai shaphang kaba mih ka sngi sha Beth-dagon, bad ka la poi haduh Sabulon, bad haduh ka them Iphtahel shaphang shatei ïa ka Beth-emek bad ka Neiel; bad ka la leit sha Kabul sha kadiang,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ka Ebron, bad ka Rehob, bad ka Hammon, bad ka Kanah, haduh ka Sidon bah;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad kata ka pud ka la phai sha Ramah, bad sha ka shnong ba la ker kynroh ka Tyros; bad ka pud ka phai sha Hosah; bad ki bakut jong ka ki don harud ka duriaw hajan ka ri Akhsib:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ka Ummah ruh, bad ka Aphek, bad ka Rehob: arphew ar ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kane ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Asher kat kum ki ïing jong ki, kine ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka bahynriew ka la hap ha ki khun u Naphtali, ha ki khun u Naphtali kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ka pud jong ki ka la long na Heleph, na uta u dieng Sning ha Saanannim, bad ka Adami-nekeb, bad ka Jabnil, haduh Lakkum; bad ki bakut jong ki, ki la long ha Jordan:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> bad kata ka pud ka phai shaphang sepngi sha Asnoth-tabor, bad ka suh nangta sha Hukkok; bad ka la poi haduh Sabulon shaphang shathie, bad ka la poi haduh Asher shaphang sepngi, bad haduh Judah ha Jordan shaphang mihngi.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ki nongbah ba la ker kynroh ki la long ka Siddim, ka Ser, bad ka Hammath, ka Rakkath, bad ka Khinnereth;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> bad ka Adamah, bad ka Ramah, bad ka Hasor;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> bad ka Kedesh, bad ka Edrei, bad ka En-hasor;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad ka Iron, bad ka Migdal-el, ka Horem, bad ka Beth-anath, bad ka Beth-shemesh: khatkhyndai ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki de.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kane ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Naphtali kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka bahynñiew ka la hap ha ka jaid ki khun u Dan kat kum ki ïing jong ki.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad ka pud ka ri kynti jong ki ka la long ka Sorah, bad ka Eshtaol bad ka Ir-shemesh;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> bad ka Shaalabbin, bad ka Aijalon, bad ka Ithlah;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> bad ka Elon, bad ka Timnah, bad ka Ekron;",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad ka Eltekeh, bad ka Gibbethon, bad ka Baalath;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> bad ka Jehud, bad ka Bene-berak, bad ka Gath-rimmon;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> bad ka Me-jarkon, bad ka Rakkon, lem bad ka pud ha pyrshah Joppa.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad ka pud ki khun u Dan ka la suh palat ïa ki: naba ki khun u Dan ki la kiew ban ïateh ïa ka Leshem, bad ki la jop ïa ka, bad ki la pom ïa ka da ka syrti waitlam, bad ki la ïoh ïa ka, bad ki la shong ha ka, bad ïa ka Leshem ki la kyrteng “Dan,” na ka kyrteng u Dan u kpa jong ki.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Kane ka long ka ri kynti ka jaid ki khun u Dan kat kum ki ïing jong ki, kine ki nongbah bad ki nongrit jong ki.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ynda ki la wai ban sam ïa ka ri ban long ka ri kynti katba kum ki pud jong ki, ki khun Israel ki la ai ri kynti ha u Joshua u khun u Nun hapdeng jong ki:",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> katba kum ka hukum U Trai ki la ai ha u ïa kata ka nongbah ba u la ïapan, ka Timnath-serah keiñ ha u lum Ephraim; bad u la tei ïa kata ka nongbah, bad u la shong ha ka.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Kine ki jingïoh kynti, kiba u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad u Joshua u khun u Nun bad ki rangbah ki kpa ki jaid ki khun Israel, ki la ïasam ban long ri kynti da ka jingkhalai ha Sheiloh ha khmat U Trai, ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng. Kumta, ki la dep kaba ïasam ïa ka ri."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la kren ha u Joshua, u da ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “To kren ha ki khun Israel, da ong, ‘To buh ha phi ïa kita ki shnong jaka rieh, kiba nga la kren ha phi da ka kti u Moses:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ba u nongpynïap briew uba kum pynïap klep ïano ïano ruh u lah ban phet ïap hangta: bad kin long ka jaka rieh jong phi na u nongpynhiar kput ka snam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad haba uta uba phet ïap ha kano kano na kita ki nongbah, un ïeng ha khmat ka khyrdop ka shnong, bad un ïathuh ïa la ka kam ha ki shkor ki tymmen basan jong kata ka shnong; te kin shim ïa u shapoh shnong ha ki, bad kin ai jaka ïa u, ba un ïoh shong hapdeng jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad lada u nongpynhiar kput ka snam un beh ïa u, te kin ym ai noh ïa uta u nongpynïap briew ha ka kti jong u; namar ba u la kum shoh ïap ïa la u paramarjan, bad um shym shun ruh ïa u mynshuwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad un shong ha kata ka shnong, ha ban da un ïeng ha khmat ka jingïaseng ban bishar, haduh ka jingïap u rangbah lyngdoh uba don ha kita ki sngi: hadien kata, uta u nongpynïap briew un leit phai noh, bad un wan sha la shnong, bad sha la ïing, sha kata ka shnong na kaba u la phet ïap.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa ka Kedesh ha Galilaïa ha u lum Naphtali, bad ïa ka Shekhem ha u lum Ephraim, bad ka Kiriath-arba (kata ka long “ka Hebron”) ha u lum Judah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad sha shiliang ka Jordan shaphang mihngi ïa ka Jerikho, ki la buh ïa ka Beser ha ri khlaw ha ka ri madan na ka jaid u Reuben, bad ïa ka Ramoth ha Gilead na ka jaid u Gad, bad ïa ka Golan ha Bashan na ka jaid u Manasseh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kine ki la long kita ki nongbah ba la buh ïa ki khun Israel baroh, bad ïa u nongwei uba shong hapdeng jong ki, ba jar uba kum pynïap ïano ïano u lah ban phet hangta, bad ba un ym ïap da ka kti u nongpynhiar kput ka snam, haduh ba ban da un ïeng ha khmat ka jingïaseng."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah ki kpa ki Lebi ki la wan hajan ha u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad ha u Joshua u khun u Nun, bad ha ki rangbah ki kpa ki jaid ki khun Israel;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ki la kren ha ki ha Sheiloh ha ka ri Kanaan, ki da ong, “U Trai u la hukum da ka kti u Moses ban ai ha ngi ki nongbah ba ngin shong, bad ki rudnong jong ki, ïa ki jingri jong ngi.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ai ha ki Lebi na kata ka jingïoh kynti jong ki, da ka hukum U Trai, ïa kine ki nongbah bad ki rudnong jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka jingkhalai ka la hap ha ka ïing ki Kohath: bad ki khun u Aaron lyngdoh, kiba long ki Lebi, ki la ïoh da ka jingkhalai na ka jaid u Judah, bad na ka jaid u Simeon, bad na ka jaid u Benjamin, khatlai ki nongbah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad kiba dang sah na ki khun u Kohath ki la ïoh da ka jingkhalai na ki ïing ka jaid u Ephraim, bad na ka jaid u Dan, bad na shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, shiphew ki nongbah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki khun u Gershon ki la ïoh da ka jingkhalai na ki ïing ka jaid u Issakhar, bad na ka jaid u Asher, bad na ka jaid Naphtali, bad na shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh ha Bashan, khatlai ki nongbah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki khun u Merari kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki la ïoh na ka jaid u Reuben, bad na ka jaid u Gad, bad na ka jaid u Sabulon, khat-ar ki nongbah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki ïa-ai da ka jingkhalai ha ki Lebi ïa kine ki nongbah bad ki rudnong jong ki, kumba U Trai u la hukum da ka kti u Moses.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la ai na ka jaid ki khun u Judah, bad na ka jaid ki khun u Simeon, ïa kine ki nongbah kiba la ong hangne da ka kyrteng:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki la long ïa ki khun u Aaron, na ki ïing ki Kohath, kiba na ki khun u Lebi: namar ka jong ki ka la long ka jingkhalai banyngkong.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la ai ha ki, ïa ka Kiriath-arba, uta u Arba u la long u kpa u Anak, (kata ka long “ka Hebron”), ha ri lum Judah, bad ki rudnong jong ka baroh sawdong.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ïa ki lyngkha jong kata ka nongbah, bad ki nongrit jong ka, ki la ai ha u Kaleb u khun u Jephunneh ban long ka jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki la ai ha ki khun u Aaron lyngdoh ïa ka Hebron bad ïa ki rudnong jong ka, ka nongbah jaka rieh ïa u nongpynïap briew, bad ïa ka Libnah bad ki rudnong jong ka;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> bad ka Jattir bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ka Eshtemoa bad ki rudnong jong ka;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ka Holon bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ka Debir bad ki rudnong jong ka;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ka Ain bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ka Juttah bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ka Beth-shemesh bad ki rudnong jong ka; khyndai tylli ki nongbah na kita ki ar jaid.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Benjamin, ïa ka Gibeon bad ki rudnong jong ka, ka Geba bad ki rudnong jong ka;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ka Anathoth bad ki rudnong jong ka, bad ka Almon bad ki rudnong jong ka; saw ki nongbah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Baroh ki shnong ki khun u Aaron, ki lyngdoh, ki la long khatlai ki nongbah bad ki rudnong jong ki.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki ïing ki khun u Kohath, ki Lebi keiñ kiba dang sah na ki khun u Kohath, ki la ïoh ki shnong ka bynta jong ki na ka jaid u Ephraim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki la ai ha ki, ïa ka Shekhem bad la ki rudnong ha u lum Ephraim, ka shnong jaka rieh ïa u nongpynïap briew, bad ïa ka Geser bad la ki rudnong;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ka Kibsaim bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Beth-horon bad la ki rudnong; saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Dan, ïa ka Eltekeh bad la ki rudnong, ka Gibbethon bad la ki rudnong;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ka Aijalon bad la ki rudnong, ka Gath-rimmon bad la ki rudnong; saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad na ki shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, ïa ka Taanakh bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Gath-rimmon bad la ki rudnong; ar tylli ki nongbah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Baroh ki shnong kiba dei ïa ki ïing ki khun u Kohath kiba dang sah ki la long shiphew bad la ki rudnong.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad ha ki khun u Gershon, na ki ïing u Lebi, na kata ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh ki la ai ïa ka Golan ha Bashan bad la ki rudnong, ka shnong jaka rieh ïa u nongpynïap briew; bad ka Beeshterah bad la ki rudnong; ar tylli ki nongbah.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Issakhar, ïa ka Kishion bad la ki rudnong, ka Daberath bad la ki rudnong;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ka Jarmuth bad la ki rudnong, ka En-gannim bad la ki rudnong; saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Asher, ïa ka Mishal bad la ki rudnong, ka Abdon bad la ki rudnong;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ka Helkath bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Rehob bad la ki rudnong; saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Naphtali, ïa ka Kedesh ha Galilaïa bad la ki rudnong, ka shnong jaka rieh ïa u nongpynïap briew, bad ka Hammoth-dor bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Kartan bad la ki rudnong; lai tylli ki nongbah.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Baroh ki shnong ki Gershon kat kum ki ïing jong ki, ki la long khatlai tylli ki nongbah bad la ki rudnong.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ha ki ïing ki khun u Merari, kiba sah na ki Lebi, na ka jaid u Sabulon, ïa ka Jokneam bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Kartah bad la ki rudnong,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ka Dimnah bad la ki rudnong, ka Nahalal bad la ki rudnong, saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Reuben, ïa ka Beser bad la ki rudnong; bad ka Jahas bad la ki rudnong,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ka Kedemoth bad la ki rudnong, bad ka Mephaath bad la ki rudnong; saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad na ka jaid u Gad, ïa ka Ramoth ha Gilead bad la ki rudnong, ka shnong jaka rieh ïa u nongpynïap briew, bad ka Mahanaim bad la ki rudnong;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> ka Heshbon bad la ki rudnong, ka Jaser bad la ki rudnong; baroh saw tylli ki nongbah.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kine ki shnong baroh kiba dei ïa ki khun u Merari kat kum ki ïing jong ki, kiba sah na ki ïing ki Lebi keiñ; ki la long da ka jingkhalai khat-ar tylli ki nongbah.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki shnong ki Lebi baroh hapdeng ka bynta ki khun Israel ki la long sawphew phra tylli ki nongbah bad la ki rudnong.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Kine ki shnong ki la long kawei pa kawei bad la ki rudnong baroh sawdong: kumta ka la long ha kine ki shnong baroh.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Kumta U Trai u la ai ha ki Israel ïa kata ka ri baroh ïa kaba u la smai ban ai ha ki kpa jong ki; bad ki la ïoh ïa ka, bad ki la shong ha ka.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Bad U Trai u la ai ha ki ka jingshongthait baroh sawdong, kat kumba u la smai baroh ha ki kpa jong ki: bad ym shym don uwei u briew na ki nongshun jong ki baroh uba la ïeng ha khmat jong ki; U Trai u la ai noh ïa ki nongshun jong ki baroh ha ka kti jong ki.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Kam shym duh ei ei na kiei kiei ki babha ïa kiba U Trai u la kren ha ka ïing Israel; ka la wan long baroh."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Joshua u la khot ïa ki Reuben, bad ïa ki Gad, bad ki shiteng jaid jong u Manasseh,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la ong ha ki, “Phi la sumar ïa baroh kaba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum ïa phi, bad phi la kohnguh ïa ka ktien jong nga baroh kaba nga la hukum ïa phi:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> phim shym iehnoh la katta sngi ïa la ki para jin haduh kane ka sngi, hynrei, phi la sumar ïa ka rukom ka hukum U Trai U Blei jong phi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mynta te, U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ai ka jingshongthait ïa ki para jong phi, kumba u la ong ïa ki: namar kata, mynta phin phai noh, bad phin leit noh sha la ki ïingjaiñ, bad ha ka ri ka bynta jong phi, ïa kaba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la ai ha phi sha shiliang ka Jordan.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, sumar bniah ban leh ïa ka hukum bad ka aiñ, kiba u Moses u shakri U Trai u la hukum ïa phi, ban ieit ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi, bad ban ïaid ha ki lynti jong u baroh, bad ban sumar ïa ki hukum jong u, bad ban snoh ha u, bad ban shakri ïa u da la ka dohnud baroh bad da la ka mynsiem baroh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la kyrkhu ïa ki, bad u la phah noh ïa ki: te ki la leit sha la ki ïingjaiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha ka shiteng ka jaid u Manasseh, u Moses u la ai ka bynta ha Bashan: hynrei, ha kata kawei pat ka shiteng, u Joshua u la ai hapdeng ki para jong ki ha kane ka liang ka Jordan shaphang sepngi. Bad haba u Joshua u la phah noh ïa ki ha la ki ïingjaiñ, u la kyrkhu ïa ki,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad u la kren ha ki, u da ong, “To phai noh sha la ki ïingjaiñ bad bun ki spah, bad ki jingri shibun eh, bad ka rupa bad ka ksiar, bad ka rnong bad ka nar, bad ki jaiñ shibun eh: to ïasam ïa ka jinglute ki nongshun jong phi bad la ki para.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad bad ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh ki la phai, bad ki la mih noh na ki khun Israel na Sheiloh, kaba ha ka ri Kanaan, ban leit sha ka ri Gilead, sha ka ri ka bynta jong ki, kaba ki la ïoh, katba kum ka ktien U Trai da ka kti u Moses.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la wan sha ki rud ka Jordan, kiba ha ka ri Kanaan, ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad bad ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh ki la tei hangta ka duwan harud ka Jordan, ka duwan kaba khraw kaba paw bha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la ïohsngew ba la ong, “Ha khmih, ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad bad ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh ki la tei ka duwan marpyrshah ka ri Kanaan, ha ki rud ka Jordan, ha kaba ki khun Israel ki la ryngkang.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba ki khun Israel ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, u paidbah ki khun Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang ha Sheiloh, ban ïaleh thma ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la phah ïa u Phinehas, u khun u Eleasar lyngdoh, ha ki khun u Reuben, bad ha ki khun u Gad, bad ha ka shiteng jaid jong u Manasseh, sha ka ri Gilead:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> lem bad u ruh shiphew ngut ki rangbah, uwei uwei u rangbah na kawei kawei ka ïing u kpa na ki jaid Israel baroh; bad uwei uwei ruh u la long u rangbah ha ka ïing ki kpa jong ki hapdeng ki hajar jong ki Israel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki la wan ha ki khun u Reuben, bad ha ki khun u Gad, bad ha ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh, ha ka ri Gilead, bad ki la ïakren bad ki, ki da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Kumne u ong u paidbah U Trai baroh, ‘Ka jingryngkang kaba kumno kane kaba phi la leh pyrshah ïa U Blei ki Israel, ban phai noh ha kane ka sngi na kaba bud ïa U Trai, ha kaba phi la tei ka duwan ha phi, ïa ka ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai ha kane ka sngi?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hato ka pop u Peor kam biang ïa ngi, na kaba ym shym la pynkhuid ïa ngi haduh kane ka sngi, la ka la ngat ka jingïapthem ruh ha u paidbah U Trai,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ba phin shu phai noh ha kane ka sngi na kaba bud ïa U Trai? bad kan long, naba phi ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai ha kane ka sngi, ba lashai un bitar ïa u paidbah Israel baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, lada ka ri ka bynta jong phi ka tngit, kumta wan sha shiliang sha ka ri ka bynta U Trai, ha kaba Ka Tabernakl U Trai ka shong, bad shim bynta hapdeng jong ngi: hynrei, wat ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai, lymne ïaleh pyrshah ïa ngi, da kaba tei ha phi kawei pat ka duwan nalor ka duwan U Trai U Blei jong ngi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Akhan u khun u Serah um shym la leh palat ha kata ka basang, bad ka jingbitar ka la hap ha u paidbah ki Israel baroh? bad uta u briew um shym la jot marwei ha la ka pop.’ ”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad bad ka shiteng jaid u Manasseh ki la ïathuh, bad ki la ong ha ki rangbah ki hajar jong ki Israel,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “U Trai, U Blei ki blei, U Trai, U Blei ki blei, u tip, bad u Israel un sa tip; lada ka long ha ka jingïaleh pyrshah, lane lada ha ka jingpalat ïa U Trai, (wat pynim ïa ngi ha kane ka sngi,)",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ba ngi la tei ka duwan ha ngi ban phai noh na kaba bud ïa U Trai; lane lada ïa ka ban ainguh halor jong ka, ka jingainguh thang lane ka jingainguh bam, lane lada ban kñia halor jong ka ki jingkñia pynïasuk, to U Trai hi un pan;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad lada ngim shym leh ïa kane da kaba leh sumar khnang, ngi da ong, ‘Lashai lashisngi ki khun jong phi ki lah ban kren ha ki khun jong ngi, da kaba ong, “Phi donkam aïu bad U Trai U Blei ki Israel?” ’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> namar U Trai u la buh ïa ka Jordan ban long ka pud hapdeng jong ngi bad jong phi, ma phi ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad keiñ; phim don ka bynta ha U Trai: kumta, ki khun jong phi kin khang ïa ki khun jong ngi ïa ka ban sheptieng ïa U Trai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar kata, ngi la ong, ‘Ïa ngin ïakhreh mynta ban tei ka duwan ha ngi, ym ïa ka jingainguh thang, lymne ïa ka jingkñia:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> hynrei, ba kan long ka sakhi hapdeng jong ngi bad jong phi, bad ki khun ki ksiew jong ngi hadien jong ngi, ba ngi lah ban shakri ïa U Trai ha khmat jong u da la ki jingainguh thang, bad da la ki jingkñia, bad da la ki jingainguh pynïasuk; ba ki khun jong phi kin ym ong ha ki khun jong ngi lashai lashisngi, “Phim don ka bynta ha U Trai.” ’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kata, ngi la ïa-ong, ‘Kan long, haba kin ong kumta ha ngi lane ha ki khun ki ksiew jong ngi lashai lashisngi, ba ngi ruh ngin ong pat, “Ha khmih, ka dur ka duwan U Trai, kaba ki kpa jong ngi ki la thaw, ym ïa ka jingainguh thang, lymne ïa ka jingkñia; hynrei, ka long ka sakhi hapdeng jong ngi bad jong phi.” ’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kaba jngai ïa ngi ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai, bad ban phai noh ha kane ka sngi na kaba bud ïa U Trai, ban tei ïa ka duwan ïa ka jingainguh thang, lane ïa ka jingainguh bam, lane ïa ka jingkñia, nalor kata ka duwan ka jong U Trai U Blei jong ngi kaba ha khmat Ka Tabernakl jong u.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba u Phinehas lyngdoh, bad ki rangbah u paidbah, kata, ki rangbah ki hajar ki Israel kiba la don ryngkat bad u, ki la ïohsngew ïa kita ki ktien kiba ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad bad ki khun u Manasseh ki la ïakren, ki la sngewbha shibun.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad u Phinehas u khun u Eleasar lyngdoh u la ong ha ki khun u Reuben, bad ha ki khun u Gad, bad ha ki khun u Manasseh, “Ha kane ka sngi ngi la tip ba U Trai u don hapdeng jong ngi, namar phim shym leh ïa kane ka jingpalat ïa U Trai: kumta, phi la pyllait ïa ki khun Israel na ka kti U Trai.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad u Phinehas u khun u Eleasar lyngdoh, bad kita ki rangbah, ki la ïaphai noh na ki khun u Reuben, bad na ki khun u Gad, na ka ri Gilead, sha ka ri Kanaan, ha ki khun Israel, bad ki la wallam ktien ha ki pat.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kata ka la pynsngewbha ïa ki khun Israel; bad ki khun Israel ki la kyrkhu ïa U Blei, bad kim shym kren shuh ban leit ïaleh thma ïa ki, ïa ka ban pynjot ïa kata ka ri ha kaba ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad ki la shong.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te ki khun u Reuben bad ki khun u Gad ki la kyrteng “ka Ed” ïa kata ka duwan: “Namar kane,” ki la ong, “ka long ka sakhi hapdeng jong ngi ba U Trai u long U Blei.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kham slem, ynda U Trai u la ai ka jingshongthait ïa ki Israel na ki nongshun jong ki baroh kylleng sawdong, u Joshua u la man tymmen bad u la hiar arsut ka rta;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u Joshua u la phah khot ïa ki Israel baroh, ïa ki tymmen basan keiñ jong ki bad ïa ki rangbah jong ki, bad ïa ki nongbishar jong ki bad ïa ki nongkam jong ki, bad u la ong ha ki, “Nga la tymmen bad nga la hiar arsut ka rta:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> phi ruh phi la ïohi ïa baroh kaba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la leh ïa kine ki jaid bynriew baroh na ka bynta jong phi; namar U Trai U Blei jong phi keiñ u long uta uba la ïaleh na ka bynta jong phi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ha khmih, nga la ïasam ha phi ïa kine ki jaid bynriew ba dang sah, ban long ki jingïoh kynti ïa ki jaid jong phi, naduh Jordan, lem bad kita ki jaid bynriew baroh ba nga la ot noh, haduh ka duriaw bad shaphang sepngi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad U Trai U Blei jong phi un beh noh ma u ïa ki ha shuwa jong phi, bad un beh noh ïa ki na khmat jong phi; bad phin ïoh ïa ka ri jong ki, kumba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ong ha phi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Namar kata, phin long shlur bha ban sumar bad ban leh ïa baroh kaba la thoh ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum u Moses, ba phin ym phai noh na ka sha kamon lane sha kadiang;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ba phin ym ïalok bad kine ki jaid bynriew, kiba dang sah hapdeng jong phi; lymne wat ong ïa ka kyrteng ki blei jong ki, lymne smai ha ki, lymne shakri ïa ki, lymne dem ïa lade ha ki:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> hynrei, to snoh ha U Trai U Blei jong phi, kumba phi la leh haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar U Trai u la beh noh na khmat jong phi ïa ki jaid bynriew bakhraw bad badonbor: hynrei ïa phi, ym shym don uwei u briew uba la ïeng ha khmat jong phi haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Uwei u briew na phi un beh ïa ki shi hajar: namar U Trai U Blei jong phi u long ma u uba ïaleh na ka bynta jong phi, kumba u la ong ha phi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, to sumar bniah ïa lade, ba phin ieit ïa U Trai U Blei jong phi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lymda kumta, lada phin phai kumno kumno ruh, bad phin snoh ha kita kiba dang sah na kine ki jaid bynriew, kine kiba dang sah hapdeng jong phi keiñ, bad phin ïashongkurim bad ki, bad phin ïaleit shapoh sha ki, bad ki sha phi:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> to tip da shisha ba U Trai U Blei jong phi un ym beh shuh ïa kine ki jaid bynriew na khmat jong phi; hynrei, kin long ki shangkhawiah bad ki jingriam ïa phi, bad ki jingsympat ha ki krung jong phi, bad ki shiah ha ki khmat jong phi, ha ban da phin duh noh na kane ka ri ka babha kaba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ai ha phi.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Ha khmih ruh, ha kane ka sngi nga leit ha ka lynti ka pyrthei baroh: bad phi ruh phi tip ha la ka dohnud baroh bad ha la ki mynsiem baroh, ba ym shym duh kawei na kita kiei kiei ki babha baroh ba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la kren shaphang jong phi; ki la jia long baroh ha phi, bad kam shym duh kawei na ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kan long, ba kumba kiei kiei baroh ki babha ki la jia ha phi ïa kiba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ong ha phi, kumta U Trai un wallam halor jong phi ïa kiei kiei ki basniew baroh, haduh ban da la pynduh noh khoit ïa phi na kane ka ri ka babha ïa kaba U Trai U Blei jong phi u la ai ha phi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Haba phin ryngkang ïa ka jutang U Trai U Blei jong phi, kaba u la hukum ïa phi, bad phin leit shakri ïa kiwei ki blei, bad phin dem ïa lade ha ki; ynda kumta, ka jingbitar U Trai kan meh pyrshah ïa phi, bad phin duh shen na kane ka ri ka babha kaba u la ai ha phi.”"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ïalum ïa ki jaid Israel baroh ha Shekhem, bad u la phah khot ïa ki tymmen basan ki Israel, bad ïa ki rangbah jong ki, bad ïa ki nongbishar jong ki, bad ïa ki nongkam jong ki; bad ki la ïeng ha khmat U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong ha u paidbah baroh, “Kumne u ong U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ‘Ki kpa jong phi ki la shong mynhyndai sha shiliang kata ka Wah, u Terah keiñ, u kpa u Abraham, bad u kpa u Nahor: bad ki la shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la shim ïa u Abraham u kpa jong phi na sha shiliang kata ka Wah, bad nga la ïalam ïa u lyngba ïa ka ri Kanaan baroh, bad nga la pynroi ïa u symbai jong u, bad nga la ai ïa u Isaak ha u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga la ai ha u Isaak ïa u Jakob bad u Iso: bad nga la ai ïa u lum Seir ha u Iso, ban ïoh ïa ka; hynrei, u Jakob bad ki khun jong u ki la leit hiar sha Ijipt.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te nga la phah ïa u Moses bad u Aaron, bad nga la pynshitom ïa ka Ijipt, katba kum kata ba nga la leh hapdeng jong ki: bad hadien kata, nga la wallam noh ïa phi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la wallam noh ïa ki kpa jong phi na Ijipt: bad phi la wan haduh ka duriaw; bad ki Ijipt ki la beh nadien ki kpa jong phi bad ki kali bad ki nongshong kulai haduh ka Duriaw Basaw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki la lynñiar ha U Trai, u la buh ka jingdum hapdeng jong phi bad ki Ijipt, bad u la wallam ïa ka duriaw halor jong ki, bad u la tyllep ïa ki; bad ki khmat jong phi ki la ïohi ïa kata kaba nga la leh ha Ijipt: bad phi la shong ha ka ri khlaw slem bah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad nga la wallam ïa phi ha ka ri ki Amor, kiba shong sha shiliang ka Jordan; bad ki la ïaleh ïa phi: bad nga la ai ïa ki ha ka kti jong phi, bad phi la ïoh ïa ka ri jong ki; bad nga la pynduh ïa ki ha khmat jong phi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, u Balak u khun u Sippor, u syiem Moab, u la ïeng ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel; bad u la phah khot ïa u Balaam u khun u Beor ban tim ïa phi:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynrei, ngam shym shahshkor ïa u Balaam; namar kata, u la kyrkhu ïa phi pynban: kumta, nga la pyllait noh ïa phi na ka kti jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad phi la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan, bad phi la wan ha Jerikho: te ki nong Jerikho ki la ïaleh ïa phi, ki Amor, bad ki Peris, bad ki Kanaan, bad ki Hit, bad ki Girgash, bad ki Hib, bad ki Jebus; bad nga la ai noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong phi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad nga la phah ïa u kyieng ha shuwa jong phi, uba la beh noh ïa ki na shuwa jong phi, ïa ki ar ngut ki syiem ki Amor keiñ: ym da ka waitlam jong me, lymne da ka ryntieh jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la ai ha phi ïa ka ri kaba phim shym la trei, bad ïa ki shnong kiba phim shym la tei, bad phi la shong ha ki; ïa ki brisoh Waiñ bad ïa ki brisoh Olib kiba phim shym la thung phi bam.’",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Mynta namar kata, to sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad to shakri ïa u ha ka jingjanai bad ha ka jingshisha: bad to iehnoh ïa kita ki blei kiba ki kpa jong phi ki la ïashakri sha shiliang kata ka Wah, bad ha Ijipt; bad to shakri phi ïa U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad lada kam idei ïa phi ban shakri ïa U Trai, to jied phi ha kane ka sngi ïano phin shakri; ïa kita kiba ki kpa jong phi ki la shakri kiba la don sha shiliang kata ka Wah, lane ïa kita ki blei ki Amor, kiba phi shong ha ka ri jong ki: hynrei, ma nga bad ka ïing jong nga ngin shakri ïa U Trai.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u paidbah u la ïathuh u la ong ruh, “Kaba eh ïa ngi ba ngin iehnoh noh ïa U Trai, ïa ka ban shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> namar U Trai U Blei jong ngi u long uta uba la wallam noh ïa ngi bad ïa ki kpa jong ngi na ka ri Ijipt, na ka ïing ka jinglongmraw, bad uba la leh ïa kita ki dak khyllah bakhraw ha khmat jong ngi, bad uba la ri pynim ïa ngi ha kata ka lynti baroh ba ngi la leit, bad hapdeng ki kynja bynriew baroh ba ngi la ïaid napdeng jong ki:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad U Trai u la beh noh na khmat jong ngi ïa ki briew baroh, ïa ki Amor keiñ kiba shong ha kata ka ri: namar kata, ngi ruh ngin shakri ïa U Trai; namar u long U Blei jong ngi.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Phi phim lah ban shakri ïa U Trai; namar u long U Blei u bakhuid; u long U Blei u bathut shen; un ym map ïa ki jingpalat lymne ïa ki pop jong phi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Lada phin iehnoh ïa U Trai, bad phin shakri ïa ki blei khyllah, ynda kumta, un phai bad un pynsniew ïa phi, bad un pynduh khoit ïa phi, hadien ba u la leh bha ïa phi.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te uta u paidbah u la ong ha u Joshua, “Em; hynrei, ngi ngin shakri ïa U Trai.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Joshua u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Phi long ki sakhi pyrshah ïa lade ba phi la jied ha lade ïa U Trai, ban shakri ïa u.” Te ki la ong, “Ngi long ki sakhi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Mynta namar kata, to iehnoh,” u la ong, “ïa kita ki blei khyllah kiba hapdeng jong phi, bad to dem ïa la ki dohnud ha U Trai U Blei ki Israel.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te uta u paidbah u la ong ha u Joshua, “Ïa U Trai U Blei jong ngi ngin shakri, bad ïa ka ktien jong u ngin kohnguh.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la pynlong ka jutang bad uta u paidbah ha kata ka sngi, bad u la buh ha ki ka aiñ bad ka rukom ha Shekhem.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Joshua u la thoh ïa kine ki ktien ha Ka Kitab Ka Hukum U Blei; bad u la shim ïa u maw bakhraw, bad u la pynïeng ïa u hangta hapoh u dieng Sning uba hajan ka jaka kyntang U Trai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad u Joshua u la ong ha uta u paidbah baroh, “Ha khmih, une u maw u long sakhi ïa ngi; namar u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien U Trai baroh ïa kiba u la kren ha ngi: namar kata, un long u sakhi ïa phi, ïoh ba phin len ïa la U Blei.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Joshua u la pyllait ïa u paidbah uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ri kynti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ka la jia ruh hadien kine kiei kiei, ba u Joshua u khun u Nun, u shakri U Trai, u la ïap noh, haba u la shispah shiphew snem ka rta,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ki la tep ïa u hapoh ka pud ka ri kynti jong u ha Timnath-serah, kaba ha ri lum Ephraim, shaphang shatei na u lum Gaash.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad ki Israel ki la shakri ïa U Trai baroh ki sngi u Joshua, bad baroh ki sngi ki tymmen basan kiba la im hadien u Joshua, bad kiba la tip ïa ki kam U Trai baroh, ïa kiba u la leh na ka bynta ki Israel.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ïa ki shyieng u Joseph, kiba ki khun Israel ki la wallam noh na Ijipt, ki la tep ha Shekhem, ha kata ka bynta ka khyndew kaba u Jakob u la thied na ki khun u Hamor u kpa u Shekhem shispah ki sbai kesitah: bad ka la jia long ka bynta ki khun u Joseph.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad u Eleasar u khun u Aaron u la ïap; bad ki la tep ïa u ha uta u lum u Phinehas u khun jong u, ïa uba la ai ha u ha ri lum Ephraim."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;